n%20October%202%2C%202023%20at%2010%3A00%20am%20at%20Churachandpur%20Police%20Station%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20cooperate%20or%20give%20a%20reply%2C%20THJ%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Court%20hence%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20arrest%20warrant%20against%20Singh.%20It%20also%20directed%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20to%20ensure%20timely%20execution%20of%20the%20order%20which%20is%20returnable%20by%20November%209%2C%202023%2C%20per%20THJ.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%208%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-meitei-leepun-pramot-singh-case-enmity%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eregistered%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20by%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20against%20Singh%2C%20regarding%20both%20tweets%20he%20and%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20posted%20online%2C%20as%20well%20as%20comments%20he%20made%20in%20an%20interview%20he%20gave%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20June%206%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20says%20that%20all%20Kukis%20would%20be%20wiped%20out%20or%20annihilated%20from%20Manipur.%20The%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20had%20reacted%20strongly%20against%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FIR%20against%20Singh%20invokes%20charges%20including%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace%20and%20criminal%20intimidation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697280154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13132622%2FKT-6-June.01_15_29_19.Still003.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnon-bailable-arrest-warrant-against-meitei-leepun-chief-pramot-singh-report%22%2C%22summary%2