worth%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20experience%20is%20invaluable%20for%20your%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20they%20often%20travel%20on%20very%20short%20notice.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20may%20not%20know%20until%2010%20minutes%20before%20that%20you're%20heading%20out%20of%20the%20country.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20have%20your%20passport%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20to%20work%20for%20elite%20clients%20who%20fly%20under%20the%20radar%20because%20they're%20not%20public-facing.%20Working%20for%20those%20families%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20relaxed%2C%20and%20travel%20plans%20tend%20to%20be%20made%20further%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221815%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tr%C3%A9%20Moment%20taking%20a%20selfie%20while%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20on%20an%20airplane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65294d0d55f52b01b35ed5c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221361%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoment%20told%20Insider%20that%20people%20looking%20to%20nanny%20for%20high-profile%20families%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20last-minute%20travel.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tr%C3%A9%20Moment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMake%20sure%20to%20set%20your%20own%20boundaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20not%20get%20overwhelmed%20in%20this%20work%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20protect%20yourself%20as%20an%20employee%20%E2%80%94%20is%20always%20to%20set%20clear%20boundaries%20and%20advocate%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20high-profile%20and%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20have%20people%20advocating%20for%20them%2C%20their%20family%2C%20and%20their%20household.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20advocate%20for%20yourself%2C%20then%20you%20will%20end%20up%20getting%20the%20short%20end%20of%20the%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20some%20of%20my%20boundaries%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20payment%20and%20timeliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20in%20my%20contracts%20a%20clause%20for%20immediate%20termination%2C%20and%20some%20of%20that%20has%20to%20do%20with%20being%20late%20on%20payments.%20A%20lot%20of%20families%20are%20not%20always%20actively%20looking%20at%20their%20checklist%2C%20and%20the%20payroll%20messes%20up%20sometimes%2C%20or%20they%20just%20don't%20pay%20you%20on%20time.%20Then%20you%20leave%20the%20house%20and%20you%20still%20haven't%20been%20paid%2C%20which%20to%20me%20is%20inappropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELateness%20is%20also%20a%20key%20issue%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%20For%20the%20employer%2C%20they're%20just%20coming%20home%20from%20work%2C%20so%20being%20late%20might%20not%20be%20on%20their%20mind%20or%20seem%20like%20a%20problem.%20They%20don't%20think%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20as%20a%20caregiver%2C%20as%20a%20care%20provider%2C%20I%20want%20to%20go%20home.%20And%20so%20sometimes%20they're%20late%205%2C%2010%2C%2015%20minutes%20here%20and%20there.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20those%2015%20minutes%20add%20up%20and%20it's%20taking%20me%20longer%20and%20longer%20to%20get%20home%2C%20and%20now%20my%20family%20is%20without%20me%20even%20longer%2C%20or%20I'm%20not%20getting%20paid%20for%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20boundary%20might%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20be%20late.%26quot%3B%20Or%2C%20it%20could%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20late%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20late%20fee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20the%20only%20person%20that%20can%20advocate%20for%20you%2C%20and%20your%20contract%20is%20the%20one%20place%20where%20you%20get%20to%20take%20care%20of%20all%20of%20your%20needs%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20end%20up%20burned%20out%2C%20upset%2C%20pissed%20off%2C%20or%20working%20for%20a%20family%20that%20does%20not%20actually%20give%20you%20what%20you%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20get%20into%20it%20for%20the%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20get-rich-quick%20career.%20Employers%20need%20to%20respect%20the%20role%20and%20pay%20fairly%2C%20but%20you%20also%20shouldn't%20get%20into%20this%20unless%20you're%20passionate%20about%20caregiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20field%20should%20be%20looked%20down%20upon.%20Some%20families%20think%20people%20just%20want%20to%20make%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20money%20doing%20this%20career%2C%20and%20they%20say%20to%20themselves%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20but%20they're%20just%20a%20nanny.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20some%20new%20nannies%20think%20to%20themselves%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20good%20with%20my%20little%20brother%20and%20sister%2C%20so%20I%20can%20do%20this%20to%20make%20money%20or%20get%20myself%20through%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20true.%20Every%20single%20family%20and%20every%20single%20child%20is%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20only%20in%20it%20to%20make%20money%20and%20not%20because%20you%20actually%20enjoy%20helping%20people%20because%20this%20is%20a%20care%20field%2C%20then%20your%20best%20bet%20is%20to%20do%20something%20that%20does%20not%20require%20you%20to%20actively%20be%20present%20in%20other%20people's%20lives%20where%20they%20have%20to%20depend%20on%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-nanny-of-wealthy-high-profile-family-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697279281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529aa6755f52b01b35f9898%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-nanny-of-wealthy-high-profile-family-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20nanny%20working%20for%20high-profile%2C%20wealthy%20families%20offers%20tips%20for%20survival%2C%20including%20setting%20boundaries%20and%20preparing%20for%20last-minute%20travel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-nanny-of-wealthy-high-profile-family-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Senior%20Journalist%20KS%20Sachidananda%20Murthy%20Passes%20Away%20at%2068%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14155040%2FF8X29BkbEAAeSx6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESenior%20journalist%20K.S.%20Sachidananda%20Murthy%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20resident%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20in%20Delhi%2C%20passed%20away%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2013.%20He%20was%2068.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Sachi%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20he%20was%20widely%20known%20in%20journalist%20circles%2C%20had%20a%20four-decade-long%20career%20in%20journalism%20and%20most%20of%20which%20was%20spent%20in%20Malayala%20Manorama%20Group%20and%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fi%3E%20magazine.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20had%20a%20stint%20with%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20served%20as%20the%20secretary%20general%20of%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Press%20Advisory%20Committee.%20He%20also%20held%20a%20stint%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Central%20Press%20Accreditation%20Committee%20and%20the%20Press%20Council%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama%3C%2Fem%3E%20ran%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20popular%20political%20column%20%3Cem%3EDesheeyam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(originally%20called%20New%20Delhi)%20on%20its%20edit%20pages%20for%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20native%20of%20Kolar%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Murthy%20was%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Media%20Academy%20Award%20for%20lifetime%20contribution%20to%20journalism.%20He%20has%20covered%20multiple%20overseas%20visits%20of%20presidents%20and%20prime%20ministers.%20%E2%80%9CSachidananda%20Murthy%20was%20among%20the%20few%20Kannadiga%20journalists%20active%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20media%20circles%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20breathed%20his%20last%2C%20Murthy%20was%20recovering%20from%20a%20recent%20lung%20transplant%20surgery%20in%20the%20city.%20He%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Findia-and-maldives-ties-despite-china-bound-by-history-and-geography-8981993%2F%5C%22%3EWriting%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20journalist%20Debashish%20Mukerji%20traces%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20professional%20trajectory%20from%20being%20a%20correspondent%20in%20Bangalore%20to%20a%20widely%20known%20and%20highly%20regarded%20journalist%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20he%20knew%20everyone%20who%20mattered%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20across%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20diplomatic%20circles.%20Correspondents%20of%20regional%20publications%20in%20Delhi%20often%20restrict%20themselves%20largely%20to%20politicians%20from%20their%20own%20state%2C%20who%20know%20their%20publications%E2%80%99%20worth%2C%20finding%20access%20challenging%20to%20those%20from%20other%20regions%2C%20who%20often%20may%20not%20have%20heard%20of%20the%20publications%20they%20represent.%20But%20Sachi%E2%80%99s%20network%20went%20way%20beyond%20Kerala%20politicians%20(or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20those%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20his%20home%20state)%2C%20embracing%20key%20players%20across%20the%20aisle%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Mukherji%2C%20who%20worked%20under%20Murthy%20whilst%20he%20was%20at%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20remembers%20Murthy%20as%20someone%20who%20rarely%20made%20political%20predictions%2C%20but%20whenever%20he%20did%2C%20he%20got%20them%20right.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20stress%20that%20describing%20Sachi%20as%20a%20purely%20political%20animal%20would%20be%20doing%20him%20a%20disservice.%20I%20was%20often%20struck%20by%20the%20sheer%20range%20of%20his%20other%20interests%2C%20though%20he%20rarely%20wrote%20about%20them%2C%20which%20included%20movies%2C%20food%2C%20travel%2C%20mythology%20and%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Mukherji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEGI%20deeply%20condoles%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20senior%20journalist%20and%20former%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Guild%2C%20Mr.%20Sachidananda%20Murthy%20(Sachi).%20He%20was%20a%20pillar%20of%20strength%20for%20the%20Guild%20and%20an%20inspiration%20for%20all%20journalists.%20Sachi%20will%20be%20dearly%20missed%20by%20all%20his%20colleagues%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20remembered%20him%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20shaped%20generations%20of%20reporters%20%26amp%3B%20his%20guidance%20was%20readily%20available%20to%20all.%20His%20charming%20ways%20easily%20won%20everyone.%20We%20all%20will%20miss%20him%20sorely.%20PCI%20pays%20its%20humble%20tributes%20to%20him%20and%20prays%20for%20eternal%20peace%20to%20his%20departed%20soul.%20Thank%20You%20Sachi%20for%20being%20part%20of%20our%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697279279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14155040%2FF8X29BkbEAAeSx6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fsenior-journalist-ks-sachidananda-murthy-passes-away-at-68%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Sachi'%2C%20as%20he%20was%20widely%20known%20in%20journalist%20circles%2C%20had%20a%20four-decade-long%20career%20in%20journalism%20and%20most%20of%20which%20was%20spent%20in%20the%20Malayala%20Manorama