nt%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20probably%20better%20than%2050%25%20back%20to%20normal%2C%20but%20probably%20not%20as%20much%20as%2075%25%20back%20to%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Fletcher%2C%20cofounder%20of%20executive%20search%20firm%20Intersection%20Growth%20Partners%2C%20told%20me%20about%20the%20volume%20of%20networking%20he's%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20line%20of%20work%20depends%20on%20networking%2C%20and%20he's%20noticed%20a%20decline%20in%20touch%20points%20across%20the%20board%2C%20including%20conference%20attendance%20and%20one-on-one%20meetups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20experts%20told%20me%20the%20way%20we%20network%20has%20changed%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20discussed%20the%20modifications%20they've%20witnessed%20and%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20%3D%20networking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22social%20media%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6387f6d7c989f000184c1dfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUdemy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Campanaro%2C%20an%20area%20director%20at%20staffing%20firm%20Adecco%2C%20told%20me%20people%20are%20finding%20commonality%20in%20a%20virtual%20world%2C%20which%20can%20then%20pivot%20into%20an%20in-person%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20pinging%20people%20on%20LinkedIn.%20We're%20getting%20friend%20requests%20on%20Facebook%2C%20engaging%20in%20tweets%2C%20liking%20pictures%20on%20Instagram%2C%20viewing%20videos%20on%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20all%20of%20that%20is%20networking%2C%26quot%3B%20Campanaro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20normalization%20of%20using%20online%20platforms%20has%20streamlined%20and%20focused%20the%20networking%20process.%20Selva%20Param%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20executive%20search%20and%20leadership%20consultancy%20firm%20Stanton%20Chase%2C%20told%20me%20people%20are%20now%20more%20responsive%20to%20cold%20DMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEver%20since%20people%20moved%20into%20hybrid%20or%20remote%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20more%20people%20are%20actually%20responsive%20towards%20direct%20messages%2C%26quot%3B%20Param%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20I%20can%20see%20more%20than%2050%25%20or%2070%25%20of%20people%20actually%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FQSPE1%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20BetterUp%20members%20seeking%20support%20from%20their%20coaches%20on%20networking%20and%20building%20relationships%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22848%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfessional%20and%20personal%20lines%20are%20blurry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShonna%20Waters%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20at%20leadership%20coaching%20platform%20BetterUp%2C%20told%20me%20more%20conferences%20are%20offering%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaters%20was%20recently%20talking%20with%20a%20parent%20about%20how%20frequently%20schools%20schedule%20events%20during%20work%20hours.%20But%20she%20emphasized%20how%20day-to-day%20interactions%20can%20also%20be%20a%20chance%20to%20network%2C%20like%20chatting%20with%20neighbors%20or%20riding%20in%20Ubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20kind%20of%20look%20for%20opportunities%20to%20get%20two-for-ones%20often%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20to%20get%20your%20objectives%20met%2C%20because%20there's%20just%20not%20necessarily%20a%20ton%20of%20discretionary%20hours%20to%20work%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Waters%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20ago%2C%20Waters%20co-founded%20a%20running%20group.%20Training%20together%20and%20attending%20social%20activities%20after%20runs%20was%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20was%20going%20on%20in%20their%20lives%20and%20how%20they%20could%20help%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20a%20lower-cost%20sport%20like%20running%20highlights%20how%20activity-based%20networking%20(not%20just%20going%20to%20a%20bar%20or%20coffee%20shop)%20has%20evolved%20beyond%20the%20golf%20course.%20Pickleball%2C%20hiking%2C%20and%20other%20pastimes%20are%20well-suited%20for%20modern-day%20networking%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20want%20to%20network%20in%20person%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20people%2C%20handshake%2C%20concept.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c0a673e1cce00181b7edb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223374%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Egremlin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20so%20much%20remote%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20lingering%20Zoom%20fatigue%20%E2%80%94%20people%20are%20keen%20for%20in-person%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20very%20few%20exceptions%2C%20people%20seem%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20getting%20together%20face-to-face%2C%26quot%3B%20Fletcher%2C%20who%20works%20in%20the%20crypto%20and%20fintech%20space%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParam%20often%20asks%20prospective%20clients%20to%20meet%20and%20connect%20to%20chat%20about%20industry%20trends.%20Before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20people%20would%20ask%20what%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20meetings%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20they're%20agreeing%20to%20meet%20up%20and%20having%20pretty%20robust%20but%20casual%20chats%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20the%20meetings%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20recruitment%20anymore%2C%20Param%20told%20me.%20People%20are%20discussing%20their%20passions%20and%20interests%20and%20how%20they%20want%20to%20impact%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20all%20are%20hum