cup-2023-virat-kohli-wears-wrong-jersey-during-india-vs-pakistan-clash-changes-it-mid-match-4480809%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Opposition%20Parties%20Submit%20Memorandum%20to%20Guv%2C%20Say%20No%20Meaningful%20Peace%20Talks%20in%20Sight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14144514%2FManipur-opposition-J.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Workers%20of%20ten%20opposition%20parties%20clashed%20with%20police%20in%20Imphal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukhrultimes.com%2Fworkers-of-10-political-parties-engage-in-scuffle-during-rally-towards-raj-bhavan%2F%5C%22%3Ewhile%20on%20their%20way%20to%20submit%20a%20memorandum%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Manipur%20governor%20Anusuiya%20Uikey%20on%20Friday%20(October%2013)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EUkhrul%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20added%20that%20there%20was%20no%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20untoward%20incident%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20party%20workers%20were%20able%20to%20deliver%20their%20memorandum.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESigned%20by%20local%20representatives%20of%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20the%20memorandum%20says%20the%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20adequately%20address%20some%20aspects%20of%20the%20ethnic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20that%20the%20Manipur%20government%20must%20lift%20prohibitory%20measures%20in%20place%20in%20the%20state%2C%20expedite%20peace%20talks%2C%20increase%20relief%20packages%20and%20arrange%20for%20the%20handing%20over%20of%20the%20bodies%20of%20two%20Meitei%20students%20whose%20death%20was%20recently%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20late%2C%20we%20have%20come%20across%20various%20prohibitory%20measures%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20prevent%20the%20citizens%20from%20exercise%20of%20their%20fundamental%20rights%20like%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20freedom%20of%20assembly%2C%20constructive%20criticism%20of%20the%20government%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20memorandum%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20vibrant%20democracy%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20proudly%20pronounce%20that%20India%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%2C%20requires%20free%20speech%20by%20individual%20and%20the%20press%2C%20criticism%20of%20the%20wrongdoing%20by%20the%20government%20to%20act%20as%20checks%20and%20balances%20on%20them%2C%20and%20freedom%20to%20peacefully%20assemble%20and%20move%20%5Bsic%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continues%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmanipur-mobile-internet-ban-extended-till-oct-16-frustration-mounts%2F1800074%2F%5C%22%3Econtinues%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20banned%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20was%20restored%20in%20September%20after%20a%20143-day-long%20blackout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-sudden-reversal-internet-shut-down-again-in-manipur%5C%22%3Ebut%20was%20shut%20down%20by%20the%20state%20government%20soon%20after%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20then%20says%20that%20there%20have%20been%20no%20meaningful%20peace%20talks%20in%20the%20state%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20early%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20agree%20that%20both%20the%20Central%20and%20state%20governments%20have%20chosen%20the%20path%20of%20non-intervention%20to%20the%20crisis%20of%20clash%20between%20the%20ethnic%20groups.%20Rather%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20sideline%20the%20main%20reasons%20behind%20the%20crisis%20by%20taking%20shelter%20to%20theory%20of%20conspiracy%20by%20outside%20militant%20organisation%20with%20intent%20to%20assault%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMemorandum%20submitted%20by%20the%20Ten%20Political%20Parties%2C%20Manipur%2C%20(AAP%2C%20AIFB%20%2CAITG%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPI(M)%2C%20INC%2C%20JD(U)%2C%20NCP%2C%20RSP%2C%20%26amp%3B%20SS(UBT)%20to%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Governor%20of%20Manipur%20today%20at%20Imphal.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fike1EHXKUc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fike1EHXKUc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20INC%20Manipur%20(%40INCManipur)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCManipur%2Fstatus%2F1712780062884266004%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20previously%20claimed%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20violence%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-govt-extends-internet-ban-till-may-26-cm-says-no-fight-between-communities%5C%22%3Enot%20due%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfight%20between%20communities%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20instead%20because%20of%20resistance%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20forest%20conservation%20and%20poppy%20clearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20tried%20to%20blame%20Kuki%20militants%20for%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20tried%20to%20start%20peace%20dialogues%20in%20June%20but%20its%20attempt%20failed%20when%20members%20from%20both%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20refused%20to%20participate%20over%20disagreements%20regarding%20the%20composition%20of%20a%20peace%20talk%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20also%20brought%20up%20the%20two%20dead%20Meitei%20students%20and%20asked%20that%20the%20state%20government%20arrange%20for%20their%20remains%20to%20reach%20their%20family%20members%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeventeen-year-old%20Luwangbi%20Linthoingambi%20Hijam%20and%2020-year-old%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20went%20missing%20in%20July%20and%20were%20confirmed%20dead%