local%20population%2C%20Modern%20Retail%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modernretail.co%2Foperations%2Fvuori-continues-its-massive-retail-expansion-as-it-targets-around-25-new-stores-a-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20also%20considers%20data%20from%20its%20wholesale%20partners%20to%20identify%20demand%20in%20a%20particular%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInside%2C%20the%20store%20is%20full%20of%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20light%2C%20even%20though%20there%20aren't%20many%20windows.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22interior%20view%20of%20Vuori%20store%20in%20Soho%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652421286e038039826d59c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20center%20of%20the%20store%20features%20an%20artificial%20skylight%20to%20give%20the%20illusion%20of%20natural%20light.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20greeted%20me%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20walked%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20was%20designed%20to%20evoke%20the%20California%20coast.%20The%20walls%20and%20tables%20are%20a%20sandstone%20color%2C%20and%20the%20floor%20is%20light%20wood.%20Potted%20plants%20adorn%20nearly%20every%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWomen's%20clothing%20lived%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20store.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20wide%20view%20of%20the%20women's%20side%20of%20the%20Vuori%20store%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652422416561dd877e74aee5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20women's%20side%20of%20the%20store.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20was%20spacious%20and%20displays%20were%20spread%20out%20%E2%80%94%20an%20intentional%20part%20of%20the%20store's%20design.%20Catherine%20Pike%2C%20the%20company's%20vice%20president%20of%20retail%2C%20told%20Modern%20Retail%20that%20newer%20stores%20would%20be%20bigger%20than%20stores%20built%20in%202020%20and%202021%20to%20give%20shoppers%20more%20space%20and%20avoid%20feeling%20crowded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20displays%20were%20clean%20but%20not%20boring.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20view%20of%20women's%20clothing%20laid%20out%20on%20tables%20at%20Vuori%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6524228d6561dd877e74af33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWomen's%20leggings%20and%20activewear%20were%20laid%20out%20on%20tables.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20section%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20table%20or%20a%20rack%2C%20followed%20a%20color%20palette%20and%20used%20a%20variety%20of%20levels%20and%20props%20to%20keep%20the%20merchandising%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sales%20associates%20were%20very%20attentive.%20Several%20were%20stationed%20around%20the%20store%20to%20check%20in%20as%20customers%20shopped.%20At%20least%20three%20approached%20me%20to%20ask%20whether%20I%20was%20finding%20everything%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20some%20business-casual%20pieces%20amid%20athletic%20apparel.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20close%20up%20of%20body%20suits%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20table%20in%20the%20Vuori%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6524235f6e038039826d5f6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWomen's%20bodysuits%20came%20in%20two%20colors%3A%20black%20and%20brown.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20pair%20of%20tailored%20pants%2C%20called%20the%20Meta%20Wideleg%2C%20that%20came%20in%20gray%2C%20black%2C%20and%20off-white.%20They%20signaled%20to%20me%20that%20the%20company%20was%20finding%20ways%20to%20transition%20from%20just%20an%20activewear%20brand%20known%20for%20supercasual%20pieces%20such%20as%20sweatpants%20to%20a%20place%20customers%20could%20also%20go%20for%20slightly%20more%20dressed-up%20looks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVuori%20has%20significantly%20expanded%20its%20product%20offerings%20since%20launching%20with%20a%20single%20pair%20of%20men's%20joggers.%20Pike%20told%20Modern%20Retail%20that%20its%20assortment%20varied%20from%20store%20to%20store%20depending%20on%20the%20local%20climate%20and%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20of%20the%20clothing%20came%20in%20neutrals%20and%20earth%20tones.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20back%20wall%20of%20sports%20bras%20and%20leggings%20with%20a%20large%20photo%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20yoga%20pose%20hung%20on%20the%20wall%20inside%20the%20Vuori%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652423ba6e038039826d60ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20back%20wall%20hung%20more%20leggings%2C%20sports%20bras%2C%20and%20shorts.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20focuses%20on%20colors%20that%20can%20easily%20complement%20customers'%20wardrobes.%20The%20BlissBlend%20leggings%20were%20so%20soft%20I%20had%20to%20try%20a%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20customers%20to%20feel%20Vuori's%20technical%20fabrics%20is%20a%20focus%20for%20the%20company.%20Nikki%20Sakelliou%2C%20its%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modernretail.co%2Fretailers%2Fin-quest-for-global-growth-vuori-opens-new-flagship-store-in-new-york-city%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModern%20Retail%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20its%20stores%20were%20popular%20with%20customers%20because%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Btouch%20and%20feel%20the%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20couldn't%20find%20my%20size%20in%20any%20of%20the%20BlissBlend%20leggings.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sports%20bras%20and%20leggings%20lie%20on%20a%20table%20with%20white%20rocks%20under%20glass%20and%20succulents%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6524241e6561dd877e74b2ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPebbles%20under%20glass%20and%20succulents%20added%20to%20the%20California%20coastal%20style%20of%20the%20store.%20%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20my%20size%2C%20an%20associate%20offered%20to%20help%20me%20and%20explained%20the%20fit.%20They%20didn't%20have%20any%20size%20small%20left%2C%20but%20she%20said%20that%20while%20most%20of%20their%20leggings%20ran%20true%20to%20size%2C%20this%20one%20was%20really%20stretchy.%20She%20suggested%20I%20could%20fit%20into%20the%20extra%20small%20if%20I%20didn't%20mind%20them%20being%20a%20little%20tighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20a%20display%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20store%20near%20the%20registers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20table%20with%20pebbles%20under%20glass%2C%20a%20large%20book%20with%20a%20model%20photo%2C%20a%20case%20with%20small%20tags%2C%20and%20a%20plaque%20describing%20the%20tags%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652425eb68f1d46f52abd3b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVuori%20puts%20inspirational%20messages%20inside%20its%20clothing.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20table%20displayed%20a%20lookbook%20and%20tags%20that%20Vuori%20placed%20in%20its%20clothing.%20A%20plaque%