ice%20Manoj%20Misra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20time%20has%20come%20when%20the%20court%20should%20impose%20exemplary%20costs%20in%20such%20frivolous%20PILs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20accordingly%20dismiss%20the%20petition%20with%20costs%20of%20Rs%205%2C00%2C000%2C%20which%20shall%20be%20deposited%20by%20the%20petitioner%20in%20the%20Registry%20of%20this%20Court%20within%20a%20period%20of%20four%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20that%20if%20the%20cost%20is%20not%20deposited%20within%20the%20aforesaid%20period%2C%20the%20same%20shall%20be%20collected%20as%20arrears%20of%20land%20revenue%20through%20the%20Collector%20and%20District%20Magistrate%20at%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20PIL%20filed%20by%20Ashok%20Pandey%20contending%20that%20he%20is%20aggrieved%20by%20what%20he%20described%20as%20a%20'defective%20oath'%20administered%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Judicature%20at%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20stated%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20did%20not%20use%20the%20expression%20%26quot%3BI%26quot%3B%20before%20his%20name%20while%20taking%20the%20oath%2C%20in%20contravention%20of%20the%20Third%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20He%20also%20contended%20that%20the%20representatives%20and%20administrator%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20and%20Dadar%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20were%20not%20invited%20to%20the%20oath%20ceremony.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697276100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fa1ooga8_supreme-court-of-india_650x400_14_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-c