e-branch%5C%22%3Emistake%20they%20had%20made%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20seeking%20separation%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20since%20they%20had%20lost%20out%20in%20the%20provision%20of%20jobs%20without%20being%20accorded%20the%20much-desired%20Schedule%206%20status%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20on%20October%209%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-assembly-mizoram-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh-rajasthan-telangana%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20dates%20for%20elections%20to%20five%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20UT%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Commission%20responded%20that%20these%20would%20be%20held%20as%20and%20when%20the%20situation%20was%20conducive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Election%20Commission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20is%20known%2C%20it%20is%20the%20constitutional%20mandate%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20ensure%20that%20freshly%20elected%20assemblies%20are%20in%20place%20in%20any%20state%20in%20which%20assemblies%20have%20either%20been%20dissolved%20or%20have%20run%20out%20their%20due%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20this%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20Commission%20seeks%20reports%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20on%20security%20details%2C%20and%20on%20obtaining%20necessary%20law%20and%20order%20infrastructure%20to%20operationalise%20elections%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresumably%2C%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20not%20yet%20conducive%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20must%20have%20been%20based%20on%20a%20report%20from%20the%20home%20ministry%2C%20one%20that%20has%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%2C%20even%20though%20no%20day%20