%3Ehuman%20growth%20hormone%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Sermorelin%2C%20Tesamorelin%2C%20and%20Ipamorelin.%20Take%20them%20before%20sleeping%2C%20when%20you%20haven't%20eaten%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20and%20they'll%20stimulate%20massive%20growth-hormone%20release%2C%20which%20can%20help%20you%20recover%20faster%20and%20improve%20fat%20loss%20and%20muscle%20repair%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20NextGen%20Health%2C%20a%20regenerative%20wellness%20clinic%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20the%20most%20common%20peptide%20treatments%20include%20CJC%201295%20%2F%20Ipamorelin%2C%20a%20blend%20of%20peptides%20that%20stimulate%20the%20production%20of%20growth%20hormone%2C%20and%20GHK-Cu%2C%20an%20anti-aging%20peptide%20for%20improving%20skin.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20think%20everybody's%20really%20excited%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lorraine%20McCarthy%2C%20a%20manager%20at%20NexGen%20Health%2C%20adding%20that%20they're%20an%20affordable%20treatment%20with%20good%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20come%20into%20the%20clinic%20for%20blood%20work%20and%20dosing%2C%20and%20are%20then%20given%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20administer%20their%20injections%20at%20home%2C%20McCarthy%20said.%20They're%20usually%20given%20a%20one%20month%20supply%20of%20their%20chosen%20treatment%2C%20which%20falls%20around%20%24420%20a%20month%2C%20she%20added.%20Prices%20for%20peptide%20shots%20generally%20fall%20in%20the%20range%20of%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20to%20close%20to%20a%20thousand%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20this%20year%2C%20Jeff%20Tang%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20technology%20startup%20accelerator%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20is%20planning%20to%20fly%20to%20Blue%20Phoenix%2C%20a%20wellness%20company%20offering%20peptide%20treatments%20in%20Medell%C3%ACn%2C%20Colombia%2C%20he%20told%20Insider%20in%20a%20message%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETang%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20tapped%20into%20Silicon%20Valley's%20biohacker%20culture%20through%20endeavors%20li