0there%20are%20plenty%20of%20drug%20and%20devices%20that%20treat%20chronic%20conditions%20related%20to%20obesity%20and%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20shares%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fozempic-wegovy-glp1-weight-loss-drugs-stock-market-winners-losers-2023-9%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3ECPAP%20manufacturers%20have%20plunged%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%2040%25%20in%20just%20a%20few%20short%20months%20as%20losing%20weight%20can%20help%20reduce%20sleep%20apnea%20patients'%20dependency%20on%20CPAP%20machines%20when%20they're%20asleep.%20Companies%20that%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fozempic-wegovy-glp1-weight-loss-drugs-stock-market-winners-losers-2023-9%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Einsulin%20delivery%20systems%20and%20diabetes%20monitoring%20devices%20have%20also%20been%20slammed%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jomes.org%2Fjournal%2Fview.html%3Fuid%3D968%26vmd%3DFull%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20GLP-1%20drugs%20can%20drive%20diabetes%20into%20remission%20for%20type-2%20diabetes%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20no%20longer%20as%20many%20intensive%20type%20two%20%5Bdiabetes%5D%20patients%20who%20need%20to%20take%20insulin%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20take%20insulin%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20need%20an%20insulin%20pump%20to%20put%20insulin%20into%20the%20body.%20So%20that's%20why%20you've%20seen%20companies%20like%20Tandem%20Diabetes%20Care%20and%20Insulet%20hit%20the%20hardest%20here%20because%20there's%20that%20direct%20link%20towards%20if%20there%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20as%20many%20patients%20taking%20insulin%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20pump%20to%20put%20insulin%20into%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Baird%20analyst%20Jeff%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20last%20month.