s.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-ozempic-wegovy-glp1-weight-loss-drugs-investing-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20are%20decades%20off%20having%20self-driving%20cars%20that%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20go%20anywhere%2C%20autonomous%20vehicle%20boss%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gavin%20Jackson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6528042b55f52b01b35ddff5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOxa%20CEO%20Gavin%20Jackson%20has%20said%20that%20self-driving%20cars%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20long%20way%26quot%3B%20from%20being%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EPiaras%20%C3%93%20M%C3%ADdheach%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOxa%20CEO%20says%20that%20the%20industry%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20long%20way%26quot%3B%20from%20self-driving%20cars%20that%20can%20operate%20anywhere.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGavin%20Jackson%20said%20collecting%20the%20huge%20amount%20of%20data%20needed%20to%20train%20vehicle%20AI%20was%20the%20main%20issue.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20car%20companies%20like%20Cruise%20and%20Tesla%20face%20questions%20over%20their%20self-driving%20tech.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFully%20self-driving%20passenger%20cars%20that%20can%20operate%20anywhere%20without%20human%20intervention%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20%26quot%3Bdecades%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20being%20a%20reality%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CEO%20of%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Google%20Cloud%20Next%20conference%20in%20London%20this%20week%2C%20Oxa%20boss%20Gavin%20Jackson%20said%20that%20the%20industry%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20long%20way%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20producing%20cars%20that%20can%20match%20or%20surpass%20human%20drivers%2C%20and%20said%20that%20such%20vehicles%20would%20need%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Blocal%20experts%26quot%3B%20before%20they%20could%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmissy-cummings-robot-taxis-tesla-elon-musk-autonomous-cruise-waymo-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etrusted%20to%20drive%20on%20public%20roads%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20space%2C%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20to%20have%20software%20that%20has%20the%20experience%2C%20the%20knowledge%2C%20and%20the%20expertise%20to%20drive%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20generalized%20AI%20that%20can%20do%20that%2C%20we're%20so%20far%20away%20from%20that.%20We%20are%20decades%20away%20from%20that%20being%20possible%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOxa%2C%20a%20UK-based%20startup%20that%20sells%20autonomous%20driving%20software%2C%20develops%20autonomous%20vehicles%20that%20travel%20on%20fixed%20routes%2C%20with%20self-driving%20features%20monitored%20by%20human%20safety%20officers.%20The%20company%20is%20focusing%20on%20urban%20public%20transport%20and%20commercial%20vehicles%2C%20rather%20than%20passenger%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20trialed%20its%20technology%20in%20refineries%2C%20solar%20farms%2C%20and%20mines%2C%20and%20has%20announced%20partnerships%20with%20autonomous%20transport%20companies%20eVerseum%20and%20Beep%20to%20integrate%20Oxa%20self-driving%20software%20into%20passenger%20shuttles%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackson%20said%20that%20the%20main%20barrier%20to%20fully%20autonomous%20vehicles%20that%20can%20drive%20themselves%20under%20any%20conditions%20was%20the%20sheer%20amount%20of%20data%20that%20would%20need%20to%20be%20collected%20to%20train%20the%20vehicle%20AI%20to%20react%20to%20every%20possible%20situation%20that%20might%20occur%20while%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgenerative-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20potential%20solution%2C%20saying%20that%20Oxa%20was%20using%20the%20technology%20to%20simulate%20a%20range%20of%20different%20scenarios%20in%20order%20to%20uncover%20potential%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20only%20so%20much%20data%20that%20you%20can%20collect%20from%20physically%20driving%20around%2C%20and%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20collect%20data%20in%20designated%20self-driving%20routes%2C%20you're%20really%20waiting%20for%20weird%20or%20dangerous%20things%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Jackson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20amount%20of%20data%20that%20you%20collect%20is%20nowhere%20near%20good%20enough%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%20to%20cater%20for%20the%20near%20infinite%20things%20that%20could%20happen%20when%20you're%20out%20driving%20%E2%80%94%20so%20you%20need%20a%20different%20way%20to%20test%20your%20software%20before%20it%20ever%20hits%20the%20road.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20around%20%26quot%3Bself-driving%26quot%3B%20vehicles%20has%20become%20increasingly%20heated%20in%20recent%20years.%20Robotaxi%20company%20Cruise%20received%20approval%20to%20operate%2024%2F7%20in%20San%20Francisco%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20but%20agreed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-slashes-robotaxi-fleet-half-after-collision-incidents-san-francisco-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecut%20its%20fleet%20of%20driverless%20taxis%20by%20half%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20several%20incidents%20of%20unmanned%20vehicles%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-driverless-car-robotaxi-runs-over-woman-san-francisco-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20involved%20in%20accidents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruises'%20robotaxis%20do%20not%20require%20a%20human%20driver%20and%20are%20capable%20of%20operating%20on%20their%20own%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20in%20certain%20circumstances%20and%20geographical%20areas.%20They%20are%20still%20some%20way%20away%20from%20the%20holy%20grail%20of%20self-driving%20cars%20%E2%80%93%20a%20vehicle%20that%20can%20operate%20anywhere%20and%20under%20any%20circumstance%20without%20any%20human%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd-beta-full-self-driving-autopilot-software-controversy-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehas%20faced%20controversy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20Tesla's%20'Full%20Self-Driving'%20feature%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20in%202016%20and%20allows%20users%20to%20automatically%20change%20lanes%2C%20recognize%20traffic%20lights%2C%20and%20park%2C%20with%20critics%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-full-self-driving-beta-videos-show-flaws-wide-release-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edeceptively%20named%20and%20suggesting%20that%20it%20poses%20a%20safety%20risk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20always%20stressed%20that%20the%20feature%20requires%20a%20licensed%20driver%20to%20monitor%20it%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-01-27%2Felon-musk-faces-sec-probe-for-role-in-tesla-self-driving-claims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBloomberg%20reported%20in%20January%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20SEC%20is%20investigating%20Elon%20Musk%20over%20comments%20made%20about%20the%20related%20Autopilot%20feature%2C%20including%20whether%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20made%20inappropriate%20statements%20about%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGavin%20Jackson%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3BLevel%205%26quot%3B%20autonomous%20vehicles%20that%20can%20operate%20on%20public%20roads%20without%20human%20interference%20are%2C%20for%20the%20moment%2C%20still%20a%20pipe%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20compared%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20self-driving%20software%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F11%2F10%2Ft-magazine%2Flondon-taxi-test-knowledge.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassing%20'The%20Knowledge'%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20famously%20difficult%20exam%20taken%20by%20London%20taxi%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20amass%20enough%20experience%20to%20know%20where%20you're%20going%2C%20know%20the%20specific%20driving%20behaviors%2C%20all%20the%20shortcuts%2C%20know%20how%20to%20get%20from%20A%20to%20B%20in%20an%20efficient%20way.%20And%20that's%20what%20self-driving%20software%20has%20to%20do%26quot%3B%20Jackson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20needs%20to%20become%20a%20local%20expert%20wherever%20it%20is%20operating%2C%20and%20over%20time%20it%20will%20eventually%20amass%20enough%20experience%20across%20all%20of%20those%20nuanced%20places%20to%20apply%20that%20to%20more%20general%20situations%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that's%20a%20long%20way%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffully-self-driving-car-tech-needs-decades-to-develop-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697274001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65280bef68f1d46f52b00dd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffully-self-driving-car-tech-needs-decades-to-develop-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oxa%20CEO%20Gavin%20Jackson%20said%20that%20the%20self-driving%20tech%20industry%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20long%20way%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20producing%20cars%20that%20can%20match%20human%20drivers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40insider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffully-self-driving-car-tech-needs-decades-to-develop-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guinness%20Book's%202024%20Edition%20Gets%20Over%2060%20Records%20From%20India.%20Details%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20edition%20of%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Records%20has%202%2C638%20achievements%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20over%2060%20from%20India%20with%20the%20entry%20on%20rainfall%20in%20Meghalaya's%20Cherrapunji%20being%20one%20of%20the%20oldest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDistributed%20in%20India%20by%20Penguin%20Random%20House%2C%20the%20book%20has%20nine%20fact-packed%20chapters%20-%20Blue%20Planet%2C%20Aquatic%20Life%2C%20Humans%2C%20Recordology%2C%20Adventures%2C%20History%2C%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20Arts%20and%20Media%2C%20and%20Sports%20-%20and%20five%20special%20features%3A%20Hall%20of%20Fame%2C%20Young%20Achievers%2C%20Gaming%2C%20Explainers%2C%20and%20Bucket%20List.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20edition%20is%20the%20final%20installment%20in%20the%20partnership%20with%20award-winning%20artist%20Rod%20Hunt.%20According%20to%20the%20publishers%2C%20completing%20the%20illustrated%20Guinness%20World%20Records%20universe%2C%20the%20cover%20artwork%20takes%20readers%20on%20a%20deep-sea%20odyssey%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20oldest%20records%20involving%20India%20is%20related%20to%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2015-16%2C%201995%2C%20Cherrapunji%2C%20a%20high-altitude%20town%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20received%202.493%20m%20(8%20ft%202%20in)%20of%20rain%20over%20the%20complete%2048-hour%20period%2C%20the%20record%20book%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20normally%20means%20that%20the%20region%20gets%20a%20high%20level%20of%20annual%20rainfall%2C%20this%20is%20the%20most%20extreme%2048-hour%20period%20on%20record%20-%20as%20verified%20by%20the%20World%20Meteorological%20Organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20calendar%20month%2C%20the%20record%20is%209%2C300%20mm%20(366%20in)%20at%20Cherrapunji%20in%20July%201861%20and%20the%2012-month%20record%20was%20also%20set%20at%20Cherrapunji%2C%20with%2026%2C461%20mm%20(1%2C041.75%20in)%20between%20August%201%2C%201860%20and%20July%2031%2C%201861%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%20Between%20August%201%2C%201860%20and%20July%2031%2C%201861%2C%20a%20total%20of%2026%2C470%20mm%20(1%2C042%20in)%20of%20rain%20fell%20at%20Cherrapunji%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Meteorological%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20record%20which%20holds%20good%20since%201937.%20It%20is%20Jalakanyaka%20(or%20Mermaid)%20by%20Indian%20sculptor%20Kanayi%20Kunhiraman%2C%20the%20largest%20sculpture%20of%20a%20merperson%20in%20the%20world.%20Reclining%20in%20a%20shell-shaped%20pool%20at%20Shankumugham%20Beach%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20concrete%20mermaid%20is%2026.5%20m%20(87%20ft)%20long%20and%207.6%20m%20(25%20ft)%20tall.%20The%20shell%20within%20which%20she%20lies%20is%20approximately%2032%20m%20(105%20ft)%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20for%20the%20first%20and%20fastest%20man%20and%20woman%20to%20have%20circumnavigated%20the%20earth%20by%20car%2C%20covering%20six%20continents%20under%20the%20rules%20applicable%20in%201989%20and%201991%20embracing%20more%20than%20an%20equator's%20length%20of%20driving%20(24%2C901%20road%20miles%3B%2040%2C075km)%2C%20is%20held%20by%20Saloo%20Choudhury%20and%20his%20wife%20Neena%20Choudhury.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20took%2069%20days%2019%20hours%205%20minutes%20from%20September%209%20to%20November%2017%2C%201989.%20The%20couple%20drove%20a%201989%20Hindustan%20%26quot%3BContessa%20Classic%26quot%3B%20starting%20and%20finishing%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20folk%20musician%20Thanga%20Darlong%20(b.%2020%20July%201920)%20was%2098%20years%20319%20days%20old%20when%20he%20was%20presented%20with%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20civilian%20award%20on%20June%204%2C%202019.%20Born%20at%20Muruai%20village%20in%20Tripura%2C%20Darlong%20is%20celebrated%20as%20the%20last%20tribal%20musician%20to%20play%20the%20'rosem'%2C%20a%20flute-like%20instrument%20made%20from%20wood%2C%20bamboo%20and%20a%20traditional%20water%20pot%20used%20by%20the%20state's%20Darlong%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shortest%20woman%20living%20is%20Nagpur's%20Jyoti%20Amge%20(born%20Dec%2016%2C%201993)%2C%20who%20measured%2062.8%20cm%20(24.7%20in).%20The%20largest%20gathering%20of%20people%20born%20prematurely%20is%20445%20and%20was%20achieved%20by%20Rainbow%20Hospitals%20India%2C%20Indian%20Foundation%20for%20Premature%20Babies%20and%20Abbott%20Healthcare%20Pvt.Ltd%20(all%20India)%20at%20the%20Park%20Hyatt%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20November%2017%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20longest-running%20sitcom%20on%20TV%20(by%20episode%20count)%20is%20%26quot%3BTaarak%20Mehta%20Ka%20Ooltah%20Chashmah%26quot%3B%20(SAB%20TV)%2C%20which%20has%20aired%203500%20episodes%2C%20as%20of%20July%202%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%2C%20tallest%20and%20most%20expensive%20private%20house%20in%20the%20world%20is%20businessman%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%2027-storey%20personal%20skyscraper%20Antilia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%201%2C154%20sites%20recognised%20by%20UNESCO%2C%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20in%20Agra%2C%20is%20currently%20the%20most%20searched-for%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20racking%20up%201.4%20million%20searches%20in%20the%20month%20of%20March%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20published%20by%20Zitango%20Travel%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20record%20holders%20include%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20J%20Jessica%20(most%20rotations%20of%20213%20of%20a%20hula%20hoop%20on%20one%20foot%20whilst%20in%20headstand%20position%20in%20one%20minute)%20and%20Rooba%20Ganesan%20(longest%20time%20of%201%20hr%2015%20min%205%20sec%20to%20hold%20the%20mermaid%20yoga%20pose)%3B%20Aditya%20Pacholi%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(largest%20turban%20of%20345.25%20m%C2%B2)%3B%20and%20Guinness%20Rishi%20(most%20flags%20tattooed%20on%20the%20body%20at%20366).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20edition's%20editor%20in%20chief%20Craig%20Glenday%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20GWR%202024%20edition%20is%20the%20end%20product%20of%20a%20year%20in%20which%20nearly%2030%2C000%20applications%20were%20reviewed%20by%20our%20records%20managers.%20Only%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20claims%20have%20made%20it%20through%20the%20selection%20process%2C%20so%20the%202%2C638%20records%20featured%20in%20the%20book%20really%20are%20the%20cream%20of%20this%20year's%20crop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20inspired%20by%20our%20Blue%20Planet%20to%20celebrate%20a%20number%20of%20underwater%20records%20-%20including%20those%20set%20by%20the%20most%20impressive%20marine%20creatures%2C%20the%20most%20adventurous%20sailors%2C%20and%20even%20the%20most%20acrobatic%20mermaids!%20-%20but%2C%20as%20ever%2C%20we've%20covered%20the%20widest%20possible%20spectrum%20of%20record-breaking%2C%20from%20the%20hairiest%20humans%20to%20the%20most%20talented%20guinea%20pigs%2C%20the%20most%20dastardly%20pirates%20to%20the%20fastest%20rollercoasters%2C%20and%20the%20best-selling%20manga%20to%20the%20most%20celebrated%20athletes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697273880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fb06mbruo_guinness-book-2024_625x300_14_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fguinness-books-2024-edition-gets-over-60-records-from-india-details-here-4480510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20edition%20of%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Records%20has%202%2C638%20achievements%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20over%2060%20from%20India%20with%20the%20entry%20on%20rainfall%20in