%20acquire%20a%20major%20shale%20producer%20for%20%2460%20billion%2C%20entrenching%20its%20future%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20for%20decades.%20%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FJessica%20Rinaldi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20no%20surprise%20that%20Exxon%20opted%20to%20buy%20Pioneer%20in%20a%20%2460%20billion%20agreement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEnergy%20analysts%20say%20fossil%20fuels%20will%20still%20account%20for%20half%20the%20world's%20energy%20mix%20by%202050.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20shows%20many%20investors%20think%20they%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20profit%20and%20protecting%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EExxonMobil's%20%2460%20billion%20bet%20that%20the%20world%20will%20be%20hooked%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20for%20decades%20is%20looking%20like%20a%20safe%20one%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Darren%20Woods%20has%20long%20said%20that%20fossil%20fuels%20will%20be%20central%20to%20the%20world's%20energy%20mix%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20The%20company's%20acquisition%20of%20Pioneer%20Natural%20Resources%2C%20the%20largest%20oil%20and%20gas%20producer%20in%20the%20Permian%20Basin%20that%20spans%20from%20West%20Texas%20into%20New%20Mexico%2C%20further%20entrenches%20Exxon%20in%20that%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20proof%20of%20Exxon's%20strategy%20to%20stay%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20van%20Baal%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20activist%20shareholder%20group%20Follow%20This%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20the%20company%20doesn't%20think%20there's%20any%20chance%20the%20world%20will%20achieve%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20because%20if%20they%20did%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20buy%20new%20assets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20200%20countries%20adopted%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20in%202016%20that%20aims%20to%20limit%20global%20temperatures%20from%20rising%20above%20catastrophic%20levels.%20Thousands%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20companies%20made%20similar%20promises.%20Yet%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20continue%20to%20rise%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarbon-emissions-2022-record-renewables-growth-solar-wind-iea-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elargely%20driven%20by%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Renewables%20like%20solar%20and%20wind%20are%20gaining%20ground%2C%20but%20not%20fast%20enough%2C%20according%20to%20climate%20and%20energy%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20majors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexxon-chevron-investors-reject-climate-change-proposals-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20under%20less%20pressure%20from%20investors%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asset%20managers%20to%20accelerate%20their%20decarbonization%20plans%20after%20earning%20record%20profits%20last%20year.%20The%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20sent%20energy%20prices%20soaring%20and%20led%20Europe%20to%20search%20for%20new%20gas%20suppliers.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20world%20is%20still%20approving%20new%20oil%20and%20gas%20projects%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpriceofoil.org%2F2023%2F09%2F12%2Fplanet-wreckers-how-20-countries-oil-and-gas-extraction-plans-risk-locking-in-climate-chaos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewith%20the%20US%20leading%20the%20way%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Big%20banks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankingonclimatechaos.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20willing%20to%20finance%20that%20expansion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20as%20they%20pledge%20to%20achieve%20net-zero%20emissions%20on%20their%20balance%20sheets%20by%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20trends%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20that%20Exxon%20opted%20to%20buy%20Pioneer.%20Many%20of%20the%20company's%20oil%20and%20gas%20fields%20are%20still%20untapped%2C%20and%20new%20wells%20pay%20back%20in%20less%20than%20two%20years%2C%20analysts%20at%20Wood%20Mackenzie%20said%20in%20a%20note.%20If%20the%20deal%20gets%20antitrust%20approval%2C%20Exxon%20would%20immediately%20double%20its%20supplies%20to%201.3%20million%20barrels%20of%20oil%20equivalent%20a%20day%2C%20with%20a%20goal%20to%20boost%20production%20to%202%20million%20barrels%20a%20day%20by%202027.%20The%20deal%20secures%20decades%20of%20supply%20for%20Exxon's%20growing%20plastics%2C%20chemicals%2C%20and%20liquified%20natural%20gas%20businesses%2C%20according%20to%20Wood%20Mackenzie%2C%20a%20global%20research%20and%20consultancy%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExxon%20already%20had%20plans%20to%20ramp%20up%20production%20in%20the%20Permian%20Basin%20before%20announcing%20the%20deal%2C%20even%20as%20Pioneer's%20CEO%20Scott%20Sheffield%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrt.com%2Fbusiness%2Foil%2Farticle%2Fpioneer-ceo-scott-sheffield-sees-looming-peak-17823129.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier%20this%20year%20predicted%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20oil%20production%20could%20peak%20in%20the%20Permian%20in%20five%20to%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20oil%20majors%20have%20resisted%20pressure%20to%20diversify%20into%20renewables%20like%20solar%20and%20wind%2C%20arguing%20that%20natural%20gas%20is%20a%20transition%20fuel%20because%20it%20produces%20fewer%20emissions%20than%20coal.%20Exxon%20has%20instead%20focused%20on%20reducing%20methane%20leaks%20along%20its%20infrastructure%20and%20developing%20nascent%20technology%20that%20captures%20carbon%20emissions%20at%20power%20plants.%20But%20those%20investments%20are%20a%20fraction%20of%20Exxon's%20spending%20on%20oil%20and%20gas%20development%20through%202027%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.exxonmobil.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-releases%2F2022%2F1208_exxonmobil-announces-corporate-plan-to-double-earnings-and-cashflow-potential-by-2027%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewill%20account%20for%20some%2070%25%20of%20capital%20expenditures%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExxon%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Energy%20Agency%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20September%20predicted%20that%20fossil%20fuels%20%E2%80%94%20which%20meet%2080%25%20of%20the%20world's%20energy%20demand%20%E2%80%94%20will%20hit%20peak%20demand%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20latest%20projections%20show%20that%20the%20growth%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20around%20the%20world%2C%20especially%20in%20China%2C%20means%20oil%20demand%20is%20on%20course%20to%20peak%20before%202030%2C%26quot%3B%20Fatih%20Birol%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20IEA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ff6155d7b-2ef7-4f62-a08a-b640b7e87fca%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20in%20an%20op-ed%20in%20the%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20fossil%20fuels%20are%20still%20expected%20to%20account%20for%20half%20of%20the%20world's%20energy%20mix%20by%202050%2C%20which%20is%20nowhere%20near%20the%20steep%20drop%20that's%20needed%20to%20hit%20global%20climate%20goals.%20Exxon%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.exxonmobil.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fglobal%2Ffiles%2Fglobal-outlook%2F2023%2F2023-global-outlook-executive-summary.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eforecast%20that%20oil%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20coal%20will%20account%20for%2068%25%20of%20the%20energy%20mix%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20that%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20analysts%20viewed%20the%20Exxon-Pioneer%20merger%20as%20a%20sign%20that%20an%20era%20of%20major%20fossil%20fuel%20growth%20is%20coming%20to%20a%20close.%20They%20predicted%20similar%20mergers%20on%20the%20horizon%20for%20other%20companies%20like%20Chevron%20and%20Shell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20deal%20is%20about%20scale%20and%20efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Logan%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20at%20Ceres%2C%20a%20sustainability%20nonprofit%20that%20works%20with%20investors%2C%20told%20Insider.%20He%20added%20that%20Exxon%20could've%20made%20a%20worse%20deal%2C%20given%20its%20clear%20track%20record%20of%20doing%20little%20to%20tackle%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20reflects%20how%20many%20investors%20think%20they%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20profits%20and%20protecting%20the%20planet%2C%20van%20Baal%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20think%20that%20shareholders%20should%20think%20again%20about%20how%20they%20deal%20with%20the%20oil%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20van%20Baal%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20consequences%20eventually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexxon-acquisition-permian-basin-pioneer-fossil-fuels-energy-transition-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697273461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652996d468f1d46f52b19734%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexxon-acquisition-permian-basin-pioneer-fossil-fuels-energy-transition-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ExxonMobil%20made%20a%20%2460%20billion%20bet%20that%20the%20world%20will%20be%20hooked%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20for%20decades.%20It%20shows%20investors%20think%20they%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20profit%20and%20the%20planet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexxon-acquisition-permian-basin-pioneer-fossil-fuels-energy-transition-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shastri's%20Boxing%20Analogy%20During%20Toss%20Leaves%20Rohit%2C%20Babar%20Amused%20-%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-pla