y-elections-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20leadership%20vacuum%20at%20the%20state%20level%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestions%20had%20surfaced%20over%20whether%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20three-term%20chief%20minister%20and%20has%20headed%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20for%2015%20years%20from%202003%20until%20the%20Congress%20trounced%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20elections%20in%202018%2C%20would%20be%20projected%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%209%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20name%20featured%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20second%20list%20which%20included%20a%20total%20of%2064%20candidates.%20Singh%20has%20been%20given%20the%20party%20ticket%20from%20Rajnandgaon.%20In%20the%20first%20list%2C%20the%20BJP%20fielded%20Durg%20MP%20Vijay%20Baghel%20to%20take%20on%20his%20uncle%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20from%20the%20Patan%20constituency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Vijay%20Baghel%20and%20him%20will%20work%20together%20while%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20will%20highlight%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20corruption%20record%20and%20make%20it%20the%20biggest%20issue%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20Baghel-led%20Congress%20government%20of%20a%20series%20of%20scams.%20This%20includes%20the%20multi-crore%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchhattisgarh-nan-pds-scam-ed-judge-accused-touch%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublic%20distribution%20system%20(PDS)%20scam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20alleged%20scam%20worth%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20Centre-sponsored%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fdel67-polls-chhattisgarh-bjp.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efree%20grains%20scheme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20launched%20to%20provide%20support%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20also%20probing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-cannot-be-a-law-unto-itself-supreme-court-says%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%202%2C161-crore%20liquor%20scam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20which%20senior%20government%20functionaries%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20their%20bail%20pleas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fchhattisgarh-hc-dismisses-regular-bail-pleas-of-four-accused-in-liquor-scam%2F665532.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erejecte%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ed%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%20as%20recently%20as%20last%20week.%20The%20incumbent%20government%20is%20also%20facing%20allegations%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvendetta-congress-ed-raid-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoal%20levy%20scam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20which%20two%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20an%20IAS%20officer%20are%20accused.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChhattisgarh%20will%20vote%20in%20two%20phases%20on%20November%207%20and%20November%2017.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2068%20seats%20to%20vote%20out%20the%20Raman%20Singh%20government%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20winning%20only%2015%20seats%20that%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Singh%20spoke%20about%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20plans%2C%20and%20the%20leadership%20questions%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20are%20the%20issues%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20focusing%20on%20in%20this%20election%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20corruption%20that%20has%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%20scams%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20from%20liquor%20to%20coal%20scam%20to%20grains%20to%20PDS%20scam.%20All%20the%20promises%20that%20they%20had%20made%20in%20their%20poll%20manifesto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20all%20incomplete%20and%20have%20not%20been%20fulfilled.%20Development%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWould%20you%20say%20that%20corruption%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20issue%20this%20election%20for%20the%20BJP%20then%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20we%20see%20corruption%20as%20the%20biggest%20issue%20that%20needs%20highlighting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Baghel%20government%20says%20that%20these%20scams%20and%20the%20probes%20that%20are%20underway%20are%20political%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvendetta-congress-ed-raid-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Evendetta.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20How%20do%20you%20see%20this%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20can%20say%20it%20is%20political%20vendetta%20but%20ED%20has%20presented%20a%2013%2C000-page%20charge%20sheets%20in%20court%20(in%20liquor%20scam%20case)%2C%20their%20senior%20IAS%20officers%20are%20in%20jail%20and%20not%20being%20given%20bail%2C%20their%20undeclared%20assets%20have%20been%20seized%2C%20cases%20are%20going%20in%20courts%20and%20yet%20they%20are%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20corruption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECongress%20is%20going%20to%20the%20people%20with%20the%20schemes%20that%20they%20have%20brought%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20and%20highlighting%20regional%20pride%20and%20%3Cem%3EChhattisgariyavaad%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BThe%20Congress%20under%20Baghel%20has%20aggressively%20promoted%20regional%20identity%20through%20this%20pitch%20through%20the%20promotion%20of%20regional%20art%2C%20culture%2C%20sports%2C%20festivals%2C%20in%20an%20ostensible%20effort%20to%20tackle%20the%20BJP-RSS%E2%80%99%20Hindutva%20pitch%20in%20the%20state%5D.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20this%20narrative%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevelopment%20has%20completely%20stopped%3B%20there%20has%20been%20no%20%3Cem%3Evikaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20state.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20Chhattisgariyavaad%20that%20they%20keep%20talking%20about%20goes%2C%20what%20Chhattisgariyavaad%20has%20Congress%20done%3F%20They%20were%20supposed%20to%20send%20three%20candidates%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20All%20three%20were%20from%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fcongress-candidates-rajeev-shukla-ranjeet-ranjan-elected-unopposed-to-rajya-sabha-from-chhattisgarh%2Farticleshow%2F91986017.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20outside%20Chhattisgarh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20people%20from%20other%20states%20were%20made%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs.%20And%20they%20are%20talking%20about%20Chhattisgariyavaad%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20not%20put%20up%20a%20CM%E2%80%99s%20face%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20You%20have%20been%20chief%20minister%20for%20three%20terms.%20But%20the%20party%20has%20not%20declared%20anyone%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20CM%E2%80%99s%20face%20yet.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20this%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20after%20the%202003%2C%202008%20and%202013%20elections%20I%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20but%20even%20at%20that%20time%20%5Bbefore%20the%20elections%5D%20no%20one%20had%20been%20declared%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20by%20the%20party.%20The%20BJP%20works%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20collective%20leadership%20and%20does%20not%20project%20any%20CM%20candidate%20ahead%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EShall%20we%20see%20you%20and%20Vijay%20Baghel%20then%20working%20together%20as%20no%20CM%20face%20has%20been%20projected%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20motto%20is%20collective%20leadership%20and%20we%20will%20all%20work%20together%20and%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20hard%20work%20will%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%20has%20decided%20to%20field%20Vijay%20Baghel%20from%20the%20Patan%20constituency%20against%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20Is%20there%20a%20caste%20calculation%20behind%20this%20to%20woo%20voters%20from%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECaste%20politics%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20for%20us.%20BJP%20has%20worked%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20the%20OBC%20community%20and%20given%20them%20importance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%20see%20the%20caste%20survey%20pitch%20being%20raised%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%3F%20They%20have%20also%20promised%20to%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcongress-state-governments-caste-and-socio-economic-surveys-cwc%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Econduct%20a%20caste%20survey%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20if%20they%20are%20re-elected%20in%20the%20state.%20Do%20you%20think%20it%20will%20have%20any%20resonance%20in%20these%20elections%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20polls%20were%20announced%20they%20remembered%20the%20caste%20survey.%20They%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20And%20before%20that%20Congress%20headed%20governments%20at%20the%20centre%20for%20years%20but%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20about%20it.%20This%20is%20being%20raked%20up%20for%20polls%20only.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20about%20tribal%20welfare%3F%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20a%20large%20tribal%20population%20(about%2030%25).%20What%20will%20be%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20for%20their%20welfare%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20has%20always%20made%20policies%20for%20the%20tribals%20and%20their%20upliftment.%20We%20have%20brought%20schemes%20to%20give%20them%20jobs%2C%20and%20bring%20them%20education.%20We%20have%20developed%20the%20entire%20infrastructure%20for%20them%20in%20Bastar%20and%20Surguja.%20Any%20development%20or%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20tribals%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20taken%20place%20during%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697272585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14140422%2FScreenshot-2023-10-14-at-2.04.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-chhattisgarh-election-raman-singh-bjp-chief-minister-face%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20Wire%2C%20the%20three-time%20CM%20spoke%20about%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20plans%2C%20and%20the%20leadership%20questions%20in%20the%20state%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-chhattisgarh-election-raman-singh-bjp-chief-minister-face%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Jungkook%20REVEAL%20V%E2%80%99s%20TikTok%20account%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697272076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104419869%2Cimgsize-31644.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fdid-bts-jungkook-accidentally-reveal-vs-tiktok-account-to-the-world%2Farticleshow%2F104419678.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104419678.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBTS%20member%20Jungkook%20has%20been%20discovered%20to%20have%20a%20secret%20TikTok%20account%2C%20and%20seems%20to%20have%20accidentally%20exposed%20another%20account%20belonging%20to%20fellow%20member%20V.%20Fan