he%20new%20Ram%20temple%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20PMO%20(Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office)%20has%20agreed%20to%20it%20but%20it%20would%20be%20unwise%20on%20our%20part%20to%20announce%20the%20chief%20guest%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20The%20PMO%20will%20announce%20it%20soon%20if%20everything%20goes%20well.%20The%20temple%20will%20be%20opened%20for%20the%20general%20public%20on%20January%2026%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20daily%20quoted%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Shree%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20had%20issued%20its%20appeal%20to%20VIPs%20without%20citing%20any%20reason.%E2%80%9DChief%20ministers%2C%20governors%2C%20ambassadors%20and%20all%20those%20who%20enjoy%20visit-and-security-related%20protocol%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20We%20or%20the%20local%20administration%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20welcome%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20trust%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20his%20office%20in%20the%20temple%20town%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2013.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20sidestepped%20questions%20if%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20was%20being%20planned%20on%20the%20said%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20devotees%20abroad%20planning%20to%20offer%20prayers%20at%20the%20temple%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20foreign%20department%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20where%20he%20said%20a%20contact%20person%20has%20been%20appointed%20for%20each%20country.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20contact%20persons%20will%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Ayodhya%20administration%20and%20fix%20a%20day%20for%20devotees%20from%20every%20county%20to%20offer%20prayers%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20a%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20holds%20great%20significance%20before%20it%20goes%20to%20polls%20next%20year%2C%20seeking%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20government.%20Construction%20of%20the%20temple%20began%20in%20November%202019%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20temple%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20(UPSCWB)%20has%20decided%20to%20change%20the%20map%20of%20the%20mosque%20that%20will%20come%20up%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Dhannipur%20village.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20allotted%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20for%20building%20the%20mosque%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20directions%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZufar%20Ahmad%20Faruqi%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20UPSCWB%20and%20chief%20trustee%20of%20the%20Indo-Islamic%20Cultural%20Foundation%2C%20said%20a%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20build%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20mosque%20complex%20will%20also%20house%20a%20300-bed%20hospital%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20mosque%20will%20begin%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Haji%20Arfat%20Shaikh%2C%20a%20BJP%20leader%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20mosque%20will%20be%20named%20Mohammad%20Ibn%20Abdullah%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697271885000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-modi-to-unveil-ayodhya-ram-temple-on-jan-22-2024-temple-trusts-appeal-sparks-speculation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shree%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20appealed%20to%20VIPs%20not%20come%20to%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20stating%20that%20authorities%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20security%20and%20protocol%20on%20that%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthew