20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20October%203%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20FIR%20filed%20by%20ACP%20Lalit%20Mohan%20Negi%2C%20of%20the%20Special%20Cell%2C%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20in%20a%20Patiala%20Court%3A%20Raids%20were%20conducted%20in%2088%20locations%2C%2081%20in%20Delhi%20and%20others%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20almost%20military-like%20proportions%20of%20Operation%20NewsClick%20signals%20the%20exceptional%20institutional%20energy%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20expended%20on%20it.%C2%A0%20There%20is%20also%20no%20mistaking%20its%20intent.%20It%20is%20a%20declaration%20that%20journalism%20can%20only%20exist%20on%20the%20terms%20set%20by%20the%20state%2C%20otherwise%20it%20will%20be%20crushed%20and%20the%20capacity%20of%20professionals%20to%20carry%20on%20with%20their%20journalistic%20work%20will%20be%20taken%20away%20from%20them%2C%20just%20like%20their%20devices%20were%20on%20October%203.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20question%20of%20warrants.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20question%20of%20receipts%20and%20hash%20values.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20a%20systematic%20dismantling%20of%20their%20capacity%20to%20think%2C%20question%2C%20reason%2C%20document%2C%20report%2C%20write%2C%20speak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20often%20resort%20to%20lazy%20terms%20to%20define%20times%20we%20are%20barreling%20through.%20We%20term%20it%20a%20second%20emergency%2C%20an%20undeclared%20emergency%2C%20a%20silent%20emergency.%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20time%20to%20search%20for%20other%20terminology%20to%20define%20the%20era.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EEmergency%20Chronicles%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Democracy%E2%80%99s%20Turning%20Point%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprofessor-gyan-prakash-emergency-totalitarianism-prabir-purkayastha%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAnalysis-%2CProf%2520Gyan%2520Prakash%253A%2520Wrong%2520to%2520Compare%25201975%2520Emergency%2520to%2520Today%2CThis%2520is%2520Way%2520More%2520Dangerous.%26amp%3Btext%3DNow%252C%2520everyone%2520who%2520thinks%2520is%2Cpenal%2520system%252C%2520with%2520no%2520rights.%5C%22%3EProf%20Gyan%20Prakash%3A%20Wrong%20to%20Compare%201975%20Emergency%20to%20Today.%20This%20is%20Way%20More%20Dangerous%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20October%205)%20believes%20there%20is%20something%20completely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esui%20generis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20present%20situation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20things%2C%20for%20him%2C%20stand%20out%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20relentless%20effort%20to%20clear%20the%20public%20sphere%20of%20any%20dissent.%20Any%20thought%20that%20deviates%20from%20what%20is%20officially%20prescribed%20is%20already%20suspect%3B%20potentially%20any%20human%20being%20who%20thinks%20is%20a%20suspect.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20attempt%20is%20to%20achieve%20a%20total%20domination%20by%20killing%20the%20juridical%20person%20in%20a%20citizen.%20This%20is%20done%2C%20he%20says%2C%20by%20%E2%80%9Ccreating%20a%20system%20of%20law%20that%20is%20outside%20the%20penal%20system%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20you%20charge%20the%20journalist%20with%20an%20anti-terror%20law%20like%20UAPA.%20This%20is%20comparable%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20to%20how%20the%20concentration%20camp%20functioned%20outside%20the%20juridical%20system.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20create%20a%20criminal%2C%20a%20terrorist%2C%20by%20completely%20killing%20all%20the%20juridical%20protection%20that%20a%20human%20being%20has%20under%20a%20system%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20go%20through%20the%20FIR%20filed%20by%20ACP%20Mohan%20Negi%2C%20a%20certain%20anxiety%20is%20writ%20large%20over%20it.%20The%20case%20is%20made%20out%20(of%20course%2C%20no%20evidence%20is%20required%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20they%20have%20UAPA%20don%E2%80%99t%20they%3F)%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20an%20organisation%20of%20modest%20proportions%2C%20based%20in%20a%20modest%20neighbourhood%20(in%20spite%20of%20the%20extravagant%20claims%20being%20made%20about%20it)%20is%20on%20the%20job%20of%20doing%20nothing%20less%20than%20disrupting%20the%20%E2%80%9Csovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20This%20fear%20is%20expressed%20at%20least%20three%20times%20in%20a%20text%20that%20is%20a%20little%20over%20a%20thousand%20words.%20Words%20like%20these%20put%20a%20genuine%20fear%2C%20not%20just%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20journalists%20reporting%20the%20story%20and%20readers%20who%20read%20or%20view%20it%2C%20but%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20judges%20called%20upon%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20have%20been%20good%20if%20this%20FIR%20had%20been%20dissected%20by%20the%20larger%20Indian%20media%2C%20those%20which%20have%20spacious%20offices%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20region%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20operate%20out%20of%20cramped%20spaces%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20great%20if%20they%20had%20tried%20to%20contextualise%20that%20irrational%20fear%20that%20Negi%20and%20his%20constabulary%20are%20expressing.%20In%20an%20earlier%20era%20that%20may%20have%20been%20possible.%20Today%20that%20police%20FIR%20has%20been%20met%20only%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20grave%20which%20unfortunately%20could%20become%20the%20right%20metaphor%20to%20describe%20the%20Indian%20media%20in%20the%20very%20near%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20why%20journalists%2C%20those%20who%20have%20the%20courage%2C%20should%20not%20allow%20themselves%20the%20luxury%20of%20ever%20forgetting%20those%2088%20knocks%20on%20the%20front%20door%20by%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04164330%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-4.32.24-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04164330%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-4.32.24-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04164330%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-4.32.24-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678257%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJournalists%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20at%20the%20release%20of%20the%20joint%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20those%20images%20from%20Gaza%20again%3A%20What%20do%20they%20tell%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsider%20some%20of%20the%20images%20of%20the%20war%20raging%20in%20Israel-Palestine%20that%20we%20have%20all%20just%20seen%20%E2%80%93%20on%20television%2C%20on%20our%20social%20media%20feeds%2C%20on%20newspaper%20pages.%20They%20throw%20us%20into%20a%20spiral%20of%20doubt%20about%20our%20very%20faculties%20of%20comprehension.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPalestine%20represents%20a%20unique%20and%20abysmal%20moral%20and%20political%20failure%20for%20the%20human%20community.%20The%20world%E2%80%99s%20major%20powers%20have%20wilfully%20allowed%20injustice%20after%20injustice%20to%20pile%20up%20against%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20beginning%20with%20that%20very%20first%20foundational%20lie%20that%20gave%20rise%20to%20Israel%3A%20A%20land%20without%20a%20people%2C%20for%20a%20people%20without%20a%20land.%20Palestine%20was%20not%20a%20land%20without%20a%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%2075%20years%20after%20the%20Nakba%20(%E2%80%98catastrophe%E2%80%99%20in%20Arabic)%20that%20visited%20Palestinians%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20world%20and%20its%20institutions%20have%20to%20ask%20themselves%20whether%20their%20human%20rights%20codes%2C%20international%20laws%20and%20conventions%2C%20are%20worth%20the%20paper%20they%20are%20on.%20As%20for%20the%20media%2C%20they%20need%20to%20ask%20themselves%20how%20much%20they%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20rubble%20that%20is%20slowly%20asphyxiating%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20by%20failing%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20as%20if%20powerful%20reportage%20has%20not%20emanated%20from%20this%20region.%20Robert%20Fisk%2C%20reporting%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20(London)%20on%20the%20massacre%20at%20Shatila%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20in%20September%201982%2C%20could%20have%20been%20reporting%20on%20the%20present%20war%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20twenty%20four%20hours%20after%20the%20massacre%E2%80%A6%20no%20one%20was%20sure%20how%20many%20had%20been%20killed.%20Down%20every%20alleyway%20there%20were%20corpses%20%E2%80%93%20women%2C%20young%20men%2C%20babies%20and%20grandparents%20%E2%80%93%20lying%20together%20in%20lazy%20and%20terrible%20profusion%E2%80%A6Each%20corridor%20through%20the%20rubble%20produced%20more%20bodies%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20story%20of%20Palestine%20has%20never%20been%20%3Cspan%3Eallowed%20a%20free%20run%20to%20yield%20up%20its%20truths.%20Those%20who%20have%20hijacked%20it%20have%20created%20and%20circulated%20their%20own%20master%20narratives%2C%20creating%20the%20conditions%20for%20the%20apartheid%20state%20that%20Israel%20has%20become%2C%20with%20its%20forced%20occupation%20and%20massacres%2C%20time%20after%20sickening%20time.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20a%20region%20of%20over%20two%20million%20people%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20being%20wiped%20out%2C%20with%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20powerful%20countries%20standing%20by%20and%20allowing%20the%20brutal%20scenario%20to%20perpetuate%20itself%20in%20the%20name%20of%20justice%20for%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20how%20is%20the%20story%20being%20framed%20today%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20analysis%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newarab.com%2Fanalysis%2Ftelling-wrong-story-palestine-western-media%5C%22%3ETelling%20the%20Palestinian%20story%3A%20An%20uphill%20battle%20against%20Western%20media%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20written%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20Palestinian%20academic%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Abeer%20Al-Najjar%2C%20points%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeditorial%20policies%20that%20%E2%80%9Cerase%20the%20huge%20power%20asymmetry%20between%20both%20parties%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20The%20very%20structures%20of%20media%20houses%20%E2%80%93%20deeply%20enmeshed%20in%20the%20foreign%20policies%20of%20the%20countries%20they%20function%20from%20%E2%80%93%20ensure%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elobally%20recognised%20journalistic%20values%20of%20accuracy%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20balance%E2%80%9D%20are%20discarded.%20News%20sources%20are%20overwhelmingly%20biased%20towards%20Israel%3B%20Palestinian%20sources%20are%20underplayed%20or%2C%20worse%2C%20the%20coverage%20consciously%20frames%20Palestine%20as%20non-human.%20In%20some%20newsrooms%2C%20even%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9CPalestine%E2%80%9D%20is%20verboten%20and%20with%20it%20is%20the%20general%20erasure%20of%20any%20awareness%20about%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20unrelenting%2C%20often%20murderous%2C%20military%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2F