Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReaders%20and%20friends%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrite%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEgregious%20assault%20on%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EJustice%20K.%20Chandru%2C%20Chennai%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CAttack%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20not%20accidental.%20It%20is%20a%20planned%20attack.%20The%20ugly%20face%20of%20fascism%20is%20once%20again%20rearing%20its%20head.%20When%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20said%20in%201975%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20vinasakale%20vibaritha%20buddhi%E2%80%9D%20(in%20times%20of%20impending%20doom%2C%20judgment%20falters)%2C%20it%20came%20to%20be%20proved%20in%20reality.%C2%A0%20After%2022%20months%20of%20the%20Emergency%20she%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20shown%20the%20door.%20Now%20we%20are%20in%20a%20period%20of%20undeclared%20emergency.%20Had%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20been%20alive%20he%20would%20have%20repeated%20that%20statement%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EDr%20Imrana%20Qadeer%2C%20former%20professor%2C%20JNU%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20assault%20on%20free%20thought%2C%20reason%20and%20independent%20thinking%20is%20the%20saddest%20thing%20that%20can%20happen%20in%20a%20democracy.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20this%20struggle!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ERam%20Ramaswamy%2C%20scientist%20and%20academic%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CPrabir%20Purkayastha%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20Indian%20democracy%20is%20deep%20and%20sustained.%20His%20voice%20cannot%20and%20should%20not%20be%20suppressed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EShabnam%20Hashmi%2C%20social%20activist%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20October%203%20raids%20on%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20homes%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20reminded%20me%20of%20some%20line%20of%20Rajesh%20Joshi%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CJo%20iss%20pagalpan%20mein%20shamil%20nahi%20hoga%2C%20mare%20jayenge%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20do%20not%20join%20this%20madness%20will%20be%20killed%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWill%20be%20put%20in%20the%20dock%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20who%20will%20speak%20in%20opposition%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20who%20speak%20the%20truth%2C%20will%20be%20killed%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20biggest%20crime%20is%20to%20be%20unarmed%20and%20innocent%20at%20this%20time%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20who%20are%20not%20criminals%2C%20will%20be%20killed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20all-round%20attack%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20its%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20its%20present%20and%20former%20employees%3B%20well-known%20journalists%20like%20Bhasha%20Singh%2C%20Abhisar%20Sharma%2C%20Urmilesh%3B%20intellectuals%20like%20Dilip%20Simeon%2C%20Sohail%20Hashmi%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%20is%20sheer%20vendetta.%20They%20have%20been%20targeted%20for%20daring%20to%20speak%20out%20and%20defy%20the%20one-sided%20narrative%20being%20pushed%20down%20our%20throats%20by%20screeching%20anchors.%20It%20is%20also%20to%20send%20a%20strong%20signal%20to%20those%20who%20are%20still%20speaking%20and%20to%20divert%20public%20attention%20away%20from%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20poverty%20and%20the%20Adani-Modi%20nexus%20exposed%20notably%20by%20former%20editor%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta.%20I%20strongly%20condemn%20this%20witch%20hunting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ELalita%20Ramdas%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Eanti-nuclear%20activist%3A%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20forward%20to%20Prabir%E2%80%99s%20recently%20published%C2%A0%20memoir%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFighting%20the%20Good%20Fight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20ventured%20to%20say%20that%20the%20outstanding%20quality%20of%20the%20man%2C%20the%20book%20and%20his%20many%20%E2%80%99good%20fights%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20the%20sense%20of%20how%20the%20personal%C2%A0and%20the%20political%20converged%20and%20blended%20so%20seamlessly.%20I%20have%20known%20him%20for%20around%20four%20decades.%20Far%20from%20encouraging%20terror%2C%20he%20epitomises%20for%20me%20integrity%2C%20compassion%C2%A0%20love%20and%20peace%E2%80%A6May%20the%20agencies%20who%20have%20taken%20you%20in%20so%20blindly%20and%20thoughtlessly%2C%20Prabir%2C%20realise%20that%20your%20gentle%20smile%2C%20deep%20intellect%20and%20loving%20heart%20will%20overcome%20and%20win%20this%20good%20fight%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EApoorvanand%2C%20professor%2C%20Delhi%20University%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Prabir%20are%20being%20punished%20for%20showing%20the%20mirror%20to%20power%20and%20telling%20truth%20to%20the%20people%20when%20Big%20Media%20is%20busy%20hiding%20it.%20They%20are%20paying%20for%20making%20peoples%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20a%20reality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EHarsh%20Mander%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20and%20human%20rights%20worker%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20age%20when%20most%20of%20the%20Indian%20media%20have%20become%20cheerleaders%20of%20power%20and%20purveyors%20of%20hate%2C%20a%20few%20beacons%20of%20integrity%20and%20courage%20remain.%20Prominent%20among%20these%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20founded%20by%20the%20redoubtable%20and%20indomitable%20Prabir.%20Fierce%20in%20his%20opposition%20to%20corporate%20capture%20and%20majoritarian%20politics%2C%20he%20stood%20firmly%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20oppressed%20of%20our%20land.%20For%20him%20to%20be%20jailed%20on%20terror%20charges%20diminishes%20us%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ESatyajit%20Rath%2C%20professor%20emeritus%2C%20IISER%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20persistent%20vindictive%20harassment%20and%20vilification%2C%20by%20multiple%20state%20agencies%2C%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20an%20organisation%2C%20and%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20personally%2C%20simply%20because%20of%20their%20legitimate%2C%20forthright%20journalism%20and%20activism%20that%20is%20critical%20of%20right-wing%20policies%2C%20politics%20and%20ideologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ERamu%20Ramdas%2C%20former%20Chief%20of%20Naval%20Staff%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%3A%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ELittle%20did%20I%20think%20that%20we%20would%20be%20witnessing%20the%20October%203%20swoop%20down%20on%20journalists%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20his%20colleague%20being%20arrested%20under%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20for%20promoting%20%E2%80%98terror%E2%80%99%3F!!%20I%20admire%20persons%20like%20him%20for%20standing%20up%20for%20their%20beliefs.%20We%20met%20for%20the%20first%20time%20when%20I%20was%20heading%20the%20Navy%20in%20the%20early%20nineties%2C%20establishing%20a%20mutual%20bond%20that%20was%20unusual%20given%20our%20polar%20opposite%20spheres.%20Prabir%20even%20interviewed%20me%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20some%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98unorthodox%E2%80%99%20choices%20I%20had%20made%20post%20my%20retirement%20in%201993!%20I%20tried%20to%20explain%20that%20I%20was%20taught%20by%20our%20civics%20teacher%20at%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Academy%2C%20that%20we%20are%20first%20and%20foremost%20citizens%20with%20primary%20responsibilities%20to%20our%20people%20and%20Constitution.%20He%20also%20taught%20us%20to%20follow%20our%20conscience%20and%20to%20be%20fearless.%C2%A0It%20is%20these%20qualities%20that%20stands%20out%20in%20Prabir.%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20this%20too%20shall%20pass%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EBezwada%20Wilson%2C%20national%20convenor%2C%20Safai%20Karmachari%20Andolan%3A%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20crushing%20of%20the%20voice%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%2C%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20like%20crushing%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20marginalised%2C%20the%20oppressed%20people%20of%20this%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20always%20covered%20those%20stories%20that%20never%20figure%20in%20the%20media.%20It%20represents%20through%20its%20work%20the%20democratisation%20of%20the%20media.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDeathly%20disinformation%20on%20Palestine%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnanya%20Ray%20writes%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20has%20been%20on%20a%20disinformation%20counter-offensive%20for%20the%20past%20several%20days%20that%20has%20been%20swallowed%20full-scale%20by%20Western%20media%20and%20complicit%20governments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20lies%20about%20the%20number%20of%20those%20killed%20(such%20as%20260%20young%20people%20in%20a%20rave-up%20on%20occupied%20land%3B%20the%20beheadings%20of%20children%3B%20the%20rape%20of%20women).%20These%20are%20issues%20that%20would%20tug%20at%20the%20hearts%20of%20any%20human%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20West%20where%20many%20consider%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Eall%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EPalestinians%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99%20and%20Hamas%20beyond%20the%20pale.%20This%20simply%20allows%20Israel%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20genocide%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Israelis%20are%20a%20huge%20asset%20to%20the%20military-industrial%20complex%20of%20the%20US%20empire%20as%20purchasers%20and%20exporters%20of%20lethal%20weapons.%20However%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20military%20states%20in%20the%20world%20as%20well%20as%20being%20the%20fifth%20nuclear%20power%20has%20made%20a%20big%20strategic%20mistake.%20If%20they%20think%20that%20wiping%20out%20the%20leadership%20of%20Gaza%20will%20help%20them%2C%20they%20are%20totally%20wrong.%20Each%20generation%20of%20children%20will%20be%20growing%20up%20even%20more%20radicalised%20having%20seen%20their%20homes%2C%20families%2C%20fathers%20mothers%2C%20brothers%2C%20and%20sisters%20blown%20up%20in%20front%20of%20them%20and%20the%20world%20looking%20the%20other%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArundhati%20Roy%3A%20Why%20now%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20that%20raises%20its%20head%20is%20precisely%20the%20one%20posed%20by%20the%20writer%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20commentary%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-is-the-indian-state-reigniting-a-13-year-old-case-against-arundhati-roy%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSaxena%2520duly%2520noted%2520that%2520a%2Cbut%2520more%2520seriously%2520of%2520sedition.%5C%22%3EWhy%20Is%20the%20Indian%20State%20Reigniting%20a%2013-Year-Old%20Case%20Against%20Arundhati%20Roy%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20(October%2011).%20The%20piece%20argues%20correctly%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20an%20elephantine%20memory.%20Nothing%20of%20these%20kinds%20of%20remarks%20is%20forgotten.%20Everything%20is%20remembered%E2%80%A6Roy%20made%20a%20speech%20in%202010.%20It%20was%20not%20forgotten.%20She%20was%20at%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20arrest%20of%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty.%20The%20FIR%20against%20her%20has%20been%20activated%20by%20the%20LG%20less%20than%20a%20week%20later.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20could%20be%20an%20additional%20reason%20for%20this%20move.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20those%20who%20comprise%20the%20Modi%20establishment%20do%20not%20just%20have%20a%20visceral%20hatred%20for%20Roy%2C%20they%20fear%20her.%20They%20fear%20her%20ability%20to%20use%20powerful%20words%20that%20sting%20them%2C%20her%20passion%20for%20justice%2C%20her%20global%20connect%2C%20her%20very%20fearlessness.%20They%20also%20fear%20that%20this%20is%20a%20writer%20who%20understands%20with%20clairvoyance%20how%20the%20carceral%20system%20works%2C%20the%20one%20they%20preside%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20character%2C%20Major%20Amrik%20Singh%2C%20who%20jumps%20out%20of%20the%20pages%20of%20her%20novel%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Utmost%20Happiness%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20may%20as%20well%20as%20been%20someone%20inhabiting%20one%20of%20the%20interrogation%20rooms%20of%20police%20departments%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmrik%20Singh%20%E2%80%98Spotter%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20was%20known%20as%2C%20for%20being%20able%20to%20spot%20the%20%E2%80%9Csnake%20in%20the%20grass%2C%20the%20militant%20hidden%20among%20a%20crowd%20of%20civilians%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20January%20of%201995%2C%20Amrik%20Singh%20had%E2%80%A6apprehended%20a%20well-known%20lawyer%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%2C%20Jalib%20Qadri%2C%20at%20a%20checkpoint%E2%80%A6Qadri%20was%20apprehended%20publicly%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20but%20the%20arrest%20was%20not%20formally%20registered%2C%20which%20was%20not%20unusual.%20There%20was%20an%20outcry%20about%20Qadri%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98abduction%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20it%20was%20thought%20prudent%20to%20release%20him.%20But%20then%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20he%20had%20disappeared.%20%E2%80%9CA%20great%20hue%20and%20cry%20arose%E2%80%A6A%20few%20days%20later%20Jalib%20Qadri%E2%80%99s%20body%20showed%20up%20in%20a%20sack%20floating%20down%20the%20Jhelum%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmrik%20Singh%20is%20a%20fictional%20character%20but%20he%20draws%20his%20substance%20from%20his%20more%20corporeal%20counterparts.%20By%20breathing%20life%20into%20him%2C%20Roy%20reminds%20us%20that%20what%20goes%20for%20%E2%80%9Claw%20and%20order%E2%80%9D%20in%20this%20country%20can%20often%20be%20a%20dystopic%20subterfuge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWrite%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697270027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F08145917%2FIMG_2074.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-newsclick-prabir-purkayastha-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-newsclick-prabir-purkayastha-palestine%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20registered%20political%20parties%20eligible%20to%20take%20part%20in%20polls%3A%20Pakistan%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697269762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104419114%2Cimgsize-11088.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fall-registered-political-parties-eligible-to-take-part-in-polls-pakistan-pm-anwaarul-haq-kakar%2Farticleshow%2F104419055.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104419055.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPakistan's%20interim%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Anwaarul%20Haq%20Kakar%2C%20has%20stated%20that%20all%20political%20parties%20registered%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%20This%20comes%20amid%20concerns%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20Imran%20Khan's%20party%2C%20the%20PTI%2C%20due%20to%20Khan's%20imprisonment.%20Kakar%20also%20ruled%20out%20talks%20with%20the%20banned%20Tehreek-i-Taliban%20Pakistan%20and%20stated%20that%20Afghan%20nationals%20residing%20in%20Pakistan%20illegally%20will%20be%20sent%20back.%20He%20expressed%20a%20desire%20for%20healthy%20ties%20with%20Kabul%2C%20but%20highlighted%20that%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20Afghan%20nationals%20are%20involved%20in%20adverse%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fall-registered-political-parties-eligible-to-take-part-in-polls-pakistan-pm-anwaarul-haq-kakar%2Farticleshow%2F104419055.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fall-registered-political-parties-eligible-to-take-part-in-polls-pakistan-pm-anwaarul-haq-kakar%2Famp_articleshow%2F104419055.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fall-registered-political-parties-eligible-to-take-part-in-polls-pakistan-pm-anwaarul-haq-kakar%2Famp_articleshow%2F104419055.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Exclusive%3A%20How%20Hamas%20%26quot%3BGalvanised%26quot%3B%20Palestinian%20Cause%2C%20But%20Lost%20Support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpalestine%5C%22%3EPalestinians%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20sought%20refuge%20in%20southern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fgaza%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Israeli%20army%20issued%20a%20warning%20about%20an%20imminent%20ground%20invasion.%20Since%20last%20week's%20surprise%20attack%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%2C%20which%20killed%20over%201%2C300%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fisrael%5C%22%3EIsrael%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20unleashed%20its%20fury%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20eradicate%20Hamas%2C%20root%20and%20stem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20escalate%20by%20the%20hour%2C%20NDTV%20spoke%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lancaster.ac.uk%2Fppr%2Fpeople%2Fsimon-mabon%5C%22%3ESimon%20Mabon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Professor%20of%20International%20Politics%20at%20Lancaster%20University%20and%20author%20of%20multiple%20books%20on%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20what%20the%20future%20might%20hold%20for%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20Will%20calling%20it%20the%20%26quot%3BIsrael-Palestine%20War%26quot%3B%20be%20a%20fair%20assessment%20of%20the%20situation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20a%20conflict%20that%20plays%20out%20within%20the%20context%20of%20societies%20beset%20by%20division.%20Israeli%20society%20is%20increasingly%20dominated%20by%20the%20right-wing%20settler%20movements%20and%20their%20political%20allies%20such%20as%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20Itamar%20Ben-Gvir%20which%20seek%20to%20shape%20Israeli%20society%20in%20accordance%20with%20their%20view.%20They%20are%20violently%20opposed%20to%20a%20strand%20of%20Palestinian%20society%20led%20by%20Hamas%20but%20which%20encapsulates%20many%20more%20in%20a%20broader%20attempt%20to%20galvanise%20the%20resistance%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20many%20Palestinians%20do%20not%20support%20Hamas.%20They%20condemn%20the%20violence%20against%20civilians.%20They%20express%20concern%20about%20Hamas's%20growing%20popularity%20as%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20political%20legitimacy%20within%20the%20West%20Bank.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20has%20captured%20support%20by%20virtue%20of%20positioning%20itself%20in%20the%20vanguard%20of%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20this%2C%20the%20conflict%20is%20consuming%20all%20parts%20of%20Palestinian%20and%20Israeli%20society%20even%20when%20it%20is%20not%20a%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20It%20is%20a%20complex%20and%20multifaceted%20conflict.%20It%20is%20a%20war%20over%20control%2C%20a%20war%20against%20terrorism%2C%20a%20struggle%20over%20occupation%2C%20and%20a%20fight%20against%20a%20system%20described%20by%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20organisations%20such%20as%20B'Tselem%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bapartheid%20system%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20Can%20Hamas%20be%20described%20as%20'freedom%20fighters'%20and%20do%20they%20accurately%20represent%20the%20overall%20Palestinian%20cause%20for%20liberation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hamas%20is%20a%20complex%20political%20entity%20that%20encompasses%20daily%20efforts%20to%20regulate%20life%20in%20Gaza%2C%20attempts%20to%20increase%20legitimacy%20and%20influence%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20a%20resistance%20component%20that%20is%20often%20captured%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20'freedom%20fighters'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20also%20uses%20tactics%20that%20have%20been%20viewed%20as%20terrorism.%20The%20killing%20of%20Israeli%20citizens%20and%20civilians%20in%20the%20past%20week%20falls%20under%20that%20banner%20of%20terrorist%20activity.%20But%20for%20Hamas%2C%20and%20for%20many%20Palestinians%2C%20it%20participates%20in%20a%20broader%20struggle%20for%20freedom%2C%20for%20liberation%2C%20and%20a%20resistance%20struggle%20against%20an%20occupation%20and%20a%2016-year-long%20blockade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20Palestinians%20do%20not%20support%20Hamas.%20They%20have%20expressed%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20Hamas%20operates%20politically%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20at%20violence%20against%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20As%20Israel%20bombs%20Gaza%20and%20Gazans%20flee%20to%20safety%2C%20how%20does%20this%20situation%20affect%20the%20West%20Bank%20which%20has%20been%20put%20under%20a%20similar%20blockade%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20have%20seen%20the%20West%20Bank%20being%20under%20occupation%20since%201967.%20We%20have%20seen%20settler%20movements%20beginning%20to%20push%20at%20the%20fabric%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%2C%20trying%20to%20expand%20into%20Palestinian%20territories.%20We%20know%20that%20they%20have%20a%20particular%20ideological%20vision%20of%20what%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20should%20look%20like%20which%20is%20illegal%20under%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Israeli%20state%20has%20pushed%20back%20against%20that%20but%20more%20recently%20with%20the%20right-wing%20government%2C%20the%20rising%20influence%20of%20hardline%20politicians%2C%20and%20the%20religious%20right%2C%20there%20has%20been%20growing%20support%20for%20settlers.%20Recently%2C%20the%20Israeli%20national%20security%20minister%20Ben-Gvir%20declared%20that%20he%20has%20purchased%2010%2C000%20assault%20rifles%20to%20be%20given%20to%20civilian%20security%20groups%2C%20including%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20continues.%20The%20regulation%20of%20life%20under%20conditions%20that%20Settler%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20continues%2C%20and%20this%20will%20almost%20certainly%20escalate%20in%20light%20of%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20in%20Gaza%20and%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20For%20those%20who%20are%20not%20familiar%2C%20how%20close%20were%20we%20to%20peace%20and%20how%20much%20of%20a%20blowback%20is%20the%20current%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20facts%20on%20the%20ground%20such%20as%20Israeli%20settler%20movements%2C%20the%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20the%20blockade%20of%20Gaza%20mean%20facts%20on%20the%20ground%20will%20prohibit%20any%20type%20of%20political%20agreement%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Oslo%20Accords.%20Until%20there%20is%20a%20curtailing%20of%20settlement%20processes%20or%20until%20there%20is%20a%20return%20of%20Palestinian%20lands%20that%20have%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20settlers%2C%20the%20scope%20for%20a%20political%20solution%20is%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20more%20vibrant%2C%20more%20legitimate%20Palestinian%20leadership.%20The%20present%20Palestinian%20Authority%20(PA)%20has%20little%20credibility.%20In%20light%20of%20that%2C%20and%20given%20the%20power%20asymmetries%2C%20peace%20is%20a%20long%20way%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20How%20much%20support%2C%20both%20civilian%20and%20political%2C%20does%20Hamas%20have%20among%20Palestinians%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hamas%20was%20elected%20in%20Gaza%20so%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20there%20and%20for%20its%20position%20against%20Israel.%20But%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20reside%2C%20there%20is%20less%20support%20and%20it%20has%20not%20managed%20to%20achieve%20the%20same%20level%20of%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20there%20were%20growing%20tensions%20between%20various%20Palestinian%20factions%2C%20and%20rising%20frustrations%20against%20Hamas's%20actions%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20But%20by%20virtue%20of%20their%20attack%2C%20and%20taking%20their%20fight%20to%20the%20occupying%20forces%2C%20they%20have%20gained%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20legitimacy%20and%20authority%20amongst%20Palestinians%20because%20they%20are%20seen%20as%20keeping%20the%20resistance%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20Does%20the%20PA%20have%20any%20real%20authority%20and%20what%20is%20their%20relationship%20now%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20people%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20PA%20wields%20very%20little%20authority%20and%20is%20unable%20to%20curtail%20any%20type%20of%20actions%20from%20Hamas%20for%20fear%20of%20condoning%20the%20occupation.%20There%20are%20no%20serious%20claims%20to%20legitimacy%20from%20actors%20within%20the%20PA%20aside%20from%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20but%20even%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20same%20level%20of%20legitimacy%20that%20others%20such%20as%20Yasser%20Arafat%20has%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20How%20can%20you%20extract%20justice%20from%20Hamas%20without%20harming%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Palestine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%20incredibly%20difficult%20because%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20urban%20landscape%20of%20Gaza.%20Hamas%20is%20firmly%20embedded%20within%20Gaza%20so%20any%20effort%20to%20extract%20forms%20of%20justice%20from%20the%20organisation%20will%20directly%20and%20indirectly%20harm%20the%20population%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20urban%20areas%20on%20the%20planet%20and%20has%20been%20under%20a%20blockade%20for%2016%20years.%20It%20has%20had%20huge%20pressure%20in%20terms%20of%20access%20to%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20food%2C%20and%20the%20basic%20infrastructure%20needed%20for%20rebuilding.%20Because%20of%20the%20dense%20population%2C%20Hamas%20is%20deeply%20embedded%20within%20daily%20life%20there.%20So%20attacks%20on%20Hamas%20will%20almost%20certainly%20incur%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20degree%20of%20how%20you%20differentiate%20between%20a%20Hamas%20operative%20or%20a%20Hamas%20sympathiser%20in%20light%20of%20the%20shift%20in%20contours%20in%20Gaza%20right%20now.%20Some%20people%20are%20standing%20up%20for%20Hamas%20because%20they%20are%20standing%20against%20Israel.%20They%20do%20not%20necessarily%20condone%20the%20actions%20of%20Hamas%20but%20in%20light%20of%20the%20occupation%2C%20the%20group%20is%20gaining%20more%20support.%20Others%20have%20taken%20up%20arms%20to%20defend%20their%20homes%20and%20families%20without%20necessarily%20supporting%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20Israel%20is%20pushing%20to%20not%20contain%20but%20obliterate%20Gaza.%20Is%20there%20any%20possibility%20of%20backing%20out%20and%20sitting%20with%20Palestinian%20leaders%20for%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20peace%20talks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20increasing%20right-wing%20nature%20of%20Israeli%20politics%2C%20the%20fragile%20nature%20of%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20latest%20coalition%2C%20and%20the%20rising%20influence%20of%20settler%20movements%20and%20the%20religious%20right%20mean%20there%20is%20little%20to%20no%20chance%20of%20Israel%20engaging%20with%20Palestinian%20leaders%20on%20peace%20or%20any%20type%20of%20political%20settlement%20without%20a%20good%20degree%20of%20international%20pressure%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20then%2C%20the%20US%20has%20professed%20widespread%20support%20for%20Israel%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20terror%26quot%3B.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20see%20widespread%20devastation%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20Is%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution%20dead%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20is%20moribund.%20Palestine%20is%20not%20recognised%20as%20a%20state%20by%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20countries%20in%20the%20international%20community.%20And%20the%20facts%20on%20the%20ground%20prohibit%20a%20diplomatic%20resolution.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20two-state%20solution%20is%20not%20viable%20until%20Palestine%20is%20recognised%20as%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20creative%20solution%20is%20needed%20to%20find%20lasting%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ.%20What%20are%20the%20wider%20implications%20of%20the%20war%20not%20just%20on%20the%20region%20but%20the%20world%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20war%20is%20having%20a%20serious%20impact%20on%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20Palestinians%20around%20the%20world%20are%20able%20to%20express%20their%20frustrations%20at%20the%20occupation.%20There%20have%20been%20calls%20to%20criminalise%20any%20type%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20support%20in%20France.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20similar%20call%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20That%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20huge%20implications%20for%20political%20expression%20and%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%2C%20and%20conversely%2C%20global%20pressure%20against%20Israel%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20occupation%20and%20the%20military%20engagement%20that%20it%20is%20undertaking%20in%20Gaza%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20is%20contributing%20in%20a%20sense%20as%20well%20to%20a%20broader%20revival%20of%20anti-Muslim%20tensions%20that%20we%20saw%20during%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20war%20on%20terror%26quot%3B.%20Similarly%2C%20anti-Semitic%20attacks%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20particularly%20worrying%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697269380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6og2sf6o_gaza-afp-_625x300_14_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-hamas-middle-east-ndtv-exclusive-how-can-hamas-be-brought-to-justice-without-harming-gazans-4480520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20have%20sought%20refuge%20in%20southern%20Gaza%20after%20the%20Israeli%20army%20issued%20a%20warning%20about%20an%20imminent%20ground%20invasion.%20Llast%20week's%20surprise%20attack%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20killed%20over%201%2C300%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-hamas-middle-east-ndtv-exclusive-how-can-hamas-be-brought-to-justice-without-harming-gazans-4480520%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-hamas-middle-east-ndtv-exclusive-how-can-hamas-be-brought-to-justice-without-harming-gazans-4480520%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-hamas-middle-east-ndtv-exclusive-how-can-hamas-be-brought-to-justice-without-harming-gazans-4480520%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Raids%20Over%2050%20Locations%20In%20Bengal%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Over%20Massive%20Passport%20Scam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20conducting%20searches%20at%2050%20locations%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Sikkim's%20Gangtok%20having%20charged%2024%20persons%20including%20government%20officials%20and%20private%20individuals%20for%20allegedly%20issuing%20passports%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20forged%20documents%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20detained%20an%20official%20posted%20in%20Gangtok%20and%20also%20a%20middleman%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20names%2024%20