n%20100%20civilians%2C%20including%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20at%20the%20Kfar%20Aza%20kibbutz%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20died%20when%20their%20homes%20were%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20they%20added.%20But%20Hamas%20disputed%20the%20account%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%20and%20false%20Israeli%20narrative%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch1%3EHow%20has%20Israel%20reacted%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20declared%20war%20on%20Hamas%20on%20Sunday%20and%20has%20since%20fired%20thousands%20of%20munitions%20at%20Gaza%20targets%2C%20flattening%20entire%20neighbourhoods%20and%20sending%20frightened%20residents%20fleeing%20for%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20army%20said%20it%20had%20conducted%20%26quot%3Blocalised%20raids%26quot%3B%20inside%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours%20%26quot%3Bto%20complete%20the%20effort%20to%20cleanse%20the%20area%20of%20terrorists%20and%20weaponry%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20these%20operations%2C%20there%20was%20also%20an%20effort%20to%20locate%20missing%20persons%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20called%20on%20residents%20of%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20including%20Gaza%20City%2C%20to%20evacuate%20their%20homes%20and%20head%20south%20%26quot%3Bfor%20their%20safety%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20heeded%20the%20call%2C%20packing%20their%20belongings%20into%20suitcases%20and%20bags%2C%20and%20leaving%20on%20foot%20or%20in%20any%20vehicle%20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20and%20others%20asked%20for%20the%20order%20to%20be%20rescinded%2C%20as%20the%201.1%20million%20people%20affected%20--%20nearly%20half%20of%20Gaza's%20entire%20population%20of%202.4%20million%20--%20had%20nowhere%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20humanitarian%20agency%20OCHA%2C%20citing%20Palestinian%20authorities%2C%20said%20more%20than%202%2C500%20homes%20have%20been%20destroyed%20or%20mad