onals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20threatened%20to%20kill%20them%20one%20by%20one%20if%20civilian%20targets%20are%20bombed%20without%20advance%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20it%20said%20at%20least%2013%20hostages%2C%20including%20foreigners%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20bombardments%20in%20the%20previous%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20said%20it%20was%20in%20contact%20with%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20to%20try%20to%20facilitate%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20ruled%20out%20negotiating%20a%20prisoner%20swap%20with%20Israel%20while%20the%20military%20operation%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGerman%20Foreign%20Minister%20Annalena%20Baerbock%2C%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Jerusalem%2C%20said%20Hamas%20was%20using%20Gaza%20residents%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshield%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20vowed%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Beverything%20in%20our%20power%26quot%3B%20to%20free%20Americans%20taken%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch1%3EIs%20the%20conflict%20limited%20to%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo.%20There%20have%20been%20days%20of%20back-and-forth%20shelling%20with%20the%20Iran-backed%20Shiite%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20on%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20with%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Reuters%20news%20agency%20said%20one%20of%20its%20video%20journalists%20was%20killed%20on%20Friday%20in%20the%20border%20area%20of%20southern%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20journalists%20were%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20earlier%20it%20was%20firing%20in%20the%20border%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20on%20Tuesday%20exchanged%20fire%20with%20militants%20in%20Syria%2C%20where%20Iran%20backs%20the%20government%2C%20after%20the%20army%20said%20munitions%20were%20fired%20towards%20the%20occupied%20Golan%20Heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Israeli%20strikes%20knocked%20out%20of%20service%20Syria's%20two%20main%20airports%20at%20Damascus%20and%20Aleppo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20ambassador%20to%20Germany%2C%20Ron%20Prosor%2C%20said%20the%20strike%20on%20Damascus%20airport%20was%20intended%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Bweapons%20deliveries%20from%20Iran%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20Israeli%20fire%20killed%20at%20least%20nine%20Palestinians%20during%20rallies%20of%20solidarity%20with%20Gazans%2C%20taking%20the%20death%20toll%20to%2044%20since%20last%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Organization%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20accused%20Israel%20of%20seeking%20to%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%20displace%20the%20Palestinian%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20seeking%20to%20shift%20%26quot%3Bthe%20humanitarian%20crisis...%20to%20neighbouring%20countries%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch1%3EWhat%20has%20Hamas%20said%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20vowed%20to%20press%20ahead%20with%20%26quot%3Bthe%20battle%20to%20liberate%20our%20land%20and%20our%20prisoners%20languishing%20in%20occupation%20prisons%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20about%205%2C000%20Palestinians%20held%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20including%20160%20children%20and%20more%20than%201%2C000%20who%20were%20detained%20without%20charge%2C%20according%20to%20a%20July%20UN%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20called%20on%20%26quot%3Bresistance%20fighters%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20in%20%26quot%3BArab%20and%20Islamic%20nations%26quot%3B%20to%20join%20the%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20rejected%20Israel's%20call%20for%20Gazans%20to%20evacuate%20the%20north%20of%20the%20enclave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20has%20the%20world%20reacted%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20led%20Western%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20with%20President%20Biden%20vowing%20%26quot%3Brock%20solid%20and%20unwavering%26quot%3B%20backing%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20delivered%20the%20message%20in%20person%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20Defence%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20adding%20further%20weight%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20sent%20additional%20military%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20including%20missiles%20for%20its%20%26quot%3BIron%20Dome%26quot%3B%20interceptor%20system%2C%20and%20is%20deploying%20hostage%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20urged%20Israel%20to%20exercise%20restraint%20and%20follow%20the%20rules%20of%20war%20in%20its%20response%2C%20while%20NATO%20said%20it%20had%20to%20do%20so%20with%20%26quot%3Bproportionality%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20is%20sending%20maritime%20patrol%20and%20surveillance%20aircraft%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20%26quot%3Bto%20track%20threats%20to%20regional%20stability%20such%20as%20the%20transfer%20of%20weapons%20to%20terrorist%20groups%26quot%3B%2C%20London%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETensions%20mounted%20with%20angry%20protests%20against%20Israel%20in%20Arab%20nations%20after%20Friday%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20celebrated%20the%20Hamas%20assault%2C%20but%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20allegations%20it%20had%20a%20role%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%2C%20pressed%20by%20Washington%20for%20months%20to%20conclude%20a%20normalisation%20agreement%20with%20Israel%2C%20denounced%20the%20displacement%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20attacks%20on%20%26quot%3Bdefenceless%20civilians%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch1%3EWhat's%20happening%20in%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%20%3Cp%3EFuel%2C%20food%20and%20water%20are%20running%20low%20in%20Gaza%20because%20of%20the%20Israeli%20strikes%20and%20siege%2C%20prompting%20calls%20for%20immediate%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20be%20sent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20shipment%20arrived%20in%20Egypt's%20Sinai%20on%20Thursday%20from%20Jordan%20but%20it%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20when%20it%20would%20get%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalls%20are%2