ss%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMythical%20beast%3F%20Boar%20rock%20at%20Bhimbetka%20showing%20a%20huge%20animal%2C%20a%20combination%20of%20boar%20and%20bull%2C%20charging%20at%20humans.%20Photo%3A%20Kavita%20Iyer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWas%20this%20image%20an%20attempt%20to%20show%20the%20huge%20odds%20they%20had%20to%20surmount%20in%20order%20to%20survive%3F%20Or%20was%20it%20an%20act%20of%20propitiating%20a%20spirit%20which%20would%20give%20them%20the%20combined%20strength%20of%20a%20boar%20and%20bull%20to%20confront%20the%20unknown%3F%20Whatever%20the%20instinct%2C%20it%20sprang%20from%20a%20close%20interaction%20with%20the%20surroundings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20visualising%20eye%20was%20breathtakingly%20evident%20was%20a%20rock%20that%20looked%20uncannily%20like%20a%20lion%E2%80%99s%20face%2C%20its%20mouth%20open%2C%20creating%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%20storey%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20a%20natural%20opening%20behind%2C%20like%20a%20window.%20In%20front%20of%20the%20rock%20was%20a%20large%20space%20closed%20from%20one%20side.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20a%20gap%C2%A0between%20two%20rocks%20seemed%20a%20well-thought-out%20entrance%20for%20a%20finely%20delineated%20earth-to-sky%20courtyard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20beginning%20of%20architecture%2C%20based%20on%20harmonising%20the%20inside%20and%20the%20outside%20and%20being%20conscious%20of%20light%20and%20shade%2C%20proof%20of%20the%20design%20eye%2C%20was%20right%20in%20front%20of%20us.%20So%20was%20the%20continuity%20of%20memory%20%E2%80%93%20from%20massive%2C%20pre-historic%20sandstone%20rock%20shelters%20to%20vast%20historic%20sandstone%20monuments%2C%20both%20never%20far%20from%20shades%20of%20nature%E2%80%99s%20green%2C%20both%20made%20luminous%20by%20the%20sunlight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etravellers%20from%20the%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0century%2C%20sat%20in%20the%20courtyard%20for%20a%20while.%20Bhimbetka%20was%20a%20charged%20space.%20It%20had%20witnessed%20the%20emerging%20shoots%20of%20human%20creativity%20born%20of%20the%20intertwined%20relationship%20between%20humans%20and%20nature.%20In%20the%20historical%20age%2C%20efflorescence%20after%20efflorescence%20of%20that%20creative%20instinct%20would%20be%20recorded%20as%20the%20history%20of%20doing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20however%2C%20the%20question%20we%20are%20asking%20ourselves%20is%20somewhat%20different%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20history%20of%20untrammelled%20doing%20poised%20to%20be%20our%20undoing%3F%20The%20question%20is%20important%20because%20the%20idea%20of%20creativity%20powering%20the%20history%20of%20doing%20in%20our%20times%20is%20marked%20by%20a%20disconnect%20between%20humans%20and%20nature.%20For%20a%20considerable%20time%20now%2C%20we%20have%20convinced%20ourselves%20that%20nature%20too%2C%20is%20a%20human%20creation.%20The%20idea%20that%20we%20exercise%20a%20hegemony%20over%20nature%20has%20spawned%20a%20creative%20instinct%20directed%20towards%20satisfying%20our%20ever-accelerating%20wants%20and%20seductive%20but%20unsustainable%20lifestyles%20by%20exploiting%20what%20we%20see%20as%20our%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20exploitation%20of%20natural%20%E2%80%98resources%E2%80%99%20is%20actually%20a%20violent%20appropriation%20that%20underpins%20inequitous%20relations%20between%20the%20powerful%20and%20the%20disadvantaged%20%E2%80%93%20between%20nations%20or%20within%20societies.%20But%20this%20act%20is%20masked%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98creative%E2%80%99%20one-size-fits-all%20narrative%20of%20development%20as%20the%20only%20panacea%20for%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20as%20the%20inter-dependent%20relationship%20between%20nature%20and%20humans%20was%20clearly%20reflected%20in%20the%20iconography%20of%20the%20Indus%20valley%20earth%20goddesses%C2%A0and%20the%20rock%20art%20of%20Bhimbetka%20even%20earlier%2C%20the%20human%20hegemony%20over%20nature%20in%20our%20times%20shows%20up%20distinctly%20in%20an%20iconography%20of%20ecological%20imbalance.%20One%20that%20we%20are%20none%20too%20keen%20to%20acknowledge%20%E2%80%93%20mountains%20of%20toxic%20waste%2C%20scarred%20forests%2C%20bodies%20hollowing%20out%20due%20to%20air%20pollution%2C%20the%20imprint%20of%20accelerating%20climate%20change%20evinced%20in%20breaking%20polar%20ice%20shelves%2C%20melting%20permafrost%2C%20rising%20temperature%20levels%2C%20frequent%20wildfires%2C%20cyclones%2C%20flash%20floods%2C%20even%20changing%20localised%20patterns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20these%20fault-lines%20of%20destruction%20crisscrossing%20our%20residence%20on%20Earth%2C%20impact%20the%20disadvantaged%20much%20more%20than%20the%20powerful%2C%20perpetuating%20inequities.%20Putting%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20survival%20of%20both%20humans%20and%20nature%2C%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20first%2C%20stringent%20Covid%20lockdown%2C%20when%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20skies%20turned%20the%20shade%20of%20Paul%20Newman%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20after%20decades%2C%20we%20were%20all%20cooped%20up%20inside%20our%20homes.%20When%20I%20ventured%20out%20after%20three%20weeks%2C%20our%20walking%20track%20was%20transformed.%20The%20crows%2C%20pigeons%2C%20mynahs%2C%20bulbuls%2C%20and%20the%20squirrels%20had%20got%20so%20used%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20humans%20that%20they%20did%20not%20scurry%20away%20as%20I%20closed%20the%20distance%20between%20us.%20The%20entire%20neighbourhood%2C%20including%20the%20swankiest%20vehicle%2C%20was%20drowning%20in%20a%20sea%20of%20dry%20crackling%20leaves%20shed%20by%20the%20trees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20short%20time%2C%20nature%20had%20reclaimed%20