could%20be%20seen%20in%20much%20closer%20quarters%20than%20Sewri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidyasagar%20can%20perfectly%20recall%20that%20Saturday%20morning%20in%20March%202016%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday.%20He%20calls%20what%20he%20saw%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98magic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20heard%20a%20loud%20noise%20as%20we%20were%20nearing%20the%20waterbody.%20It%20was%20the%20sound%20of%20thousands%20of%20flamingos%20cackling.%20The%20rising%20sun%20painted%20the%20murky%20tidal%20waters%20and%20the%20pink%20birds%20golden.%20I%20was%20enamoured%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2047-year-old.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsodrLsyPCz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsodrLsyPCz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsodrLsyPCz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%F0%9D%9A%85%F0%9D%9A%92%F0%9D%9A%8D%F0%9D%9A%A2%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9C%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%90%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9B%20%F0%9D%99%B7%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9B%F0%9D%9A%92%F0%9D%9A%91%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9B%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%97%20(%40flamingosofmumbai)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20an%20interest%20in%20photography%20and%20birds%2C%20Vidyasagar%20then%20invested%20in%20a%20good%20camera%20and%20began%20visiting%20the%20wetlands%20every%20week.%20He%20also%20started%20extensive%20research%20on%20the%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20flamingos%20began%20visiting%20Mumbai%20in%20the%201990s.%20A%20Bombay%20Natural%20History%20Society%20(BNHS)%20study%20found%201.2%20lakh%20Greater%20and%20Lesser%20flamingos%20(two%20species)%20in%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%94%20mainly%20the%20Thane%20creek%20%E2%80%94%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThane%20creek%2C%20which%20separates%20Mumbai%20island%20from%20the%20mainland%20is%20the%20key%20to%20this%20ecosystem%20and%20here%20is%20where%20the%20flamingos%20arrive%20from%20Kutch%20and%20some%20probably%20(the%20greater%20flamingos)%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20Persian%20gulf.%20Mumbai%20has%20such%20a%20beautiful%20mangrove%20and%20wetland%20habitat%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vidyasagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVisiting%20the%20numerous%20wetlands%20in%20the%20city%20and%20documenting%20the%20beautiful%20birds%20led%20to%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20about%20the%20issues%20around%20wetlands%20and%20the%20natural%20history%20phenomenon.%20He%20decided%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20conserving%20the%20urban%20wetlands%20through%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fflamingosofmumbai%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20page.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E