nd%20lake%20is%20amongst%20the%20three%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20that%20are%20crucial%20for%20flamingo%20migration.%20They%20come%20here%20during%20high%20tides%20and%20perform%20their%20mating%20dance%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20photographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20Complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332211%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EImage%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20Vidyasagar%E2%80%99s%20first%20pictures%2C%20taken%20in%202016%2C%20during%20sunrise.%20He%20explains%20that%20flamingos%20are%20a%20very%20good%20indicator%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%