aster%3A%20Dam%20Site%20%E2%80%98Completely%20Devastated%E2%80%99%2C%20Full%20Extent%20of%20Loss%20Will%20Take%20Days%20To%20Assess%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20dam%20site%20area%20of%20Teesta-III%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20devastated%E2%80%9D%20and%20it%20will%20take%20at%20least%2010-20%20days%20to%20assess%20the%20actual%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20property%20caused%20by%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20dam%20in%20Chungthang%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20local%20activists%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20affected%20areas%20of%20Sikkim%20said%20in%20an%20online%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20October%2012.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20natural%20disaster%20as%20the%20state%20government%20claims%2C%20but%20a%20man-made%20one%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Teesta-III%20dam%20was%20swept%20away%20on%20October%204%20due%20to%20the%20bursting%20of%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20glacial%20lake%20upstream.%20The%20event%20caused%20widespread%20devastation%20downstream%20of%20the%20dam.%20As%20per%20some%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsikkim-flash-flood-toll-rises-to-37-inclement-weather-hampers-air-evacuation%2F668937.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20nearly%2040%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20nearly%2080%20are%20missing.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20experts%20on%20dam%20safety%20said%20that%20an%20early%20warning%20system%20and%20better%20operation%20of%20the%20dam%2C%20among%20other%20factors%2C%20could%20have%20decreased%20the%20devastation%20caused%20by%20the%20disaster.%20Activists%20have%20planned%20%E2%80%9CNational%20Climate%20Strikes%E2%80%9D%20on%20October%2015%20to%20express%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2012%2C%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(NDMA)%20declared%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20Automated%20Weather%20Station%20it%20had%20installed%20on%20September%2016%20in%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20had%20stopped%20working%20on%20September%2019.%20It%20now%20recommends%20that%20the%20GLOF%20Risk%20Mitigation%20Programme%20be%20%E2%80%9Cextended%20to%20high-risk%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CDamsite%20completely%20devastated%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn-ground%20relief%20work%20is%20being%20conducted%20by%20the%20government%3B%20however%2C%20north%20Sikkim%20as%20well%20as%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20dam%20site%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Chungthang%20town%20is%20%E2%80%93%20are%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20devastated%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Gyatso%20Lepcha%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Affected%20Citizens%20of%20Teesta%20(ACT)%2C%20an%20organisation%20of%20the%20indigenous%20Lepcha%20community%20which%20has%20been%20opposing%20the%20construction%20of%20large%20dams%20in%20the%20state%20for%20a%20decade%20now.%20Towns%20downstream%20and%20near%20the%20river%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cwashed%20out%E2%80%9D%2C%20Lepcha%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EExclusive%20visuals%20from%20completely%20damaged%20Chungthang%20Dam%20in%20Sikkim%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReceived%20from%20Pokhraj%20Rai%20Ji%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fx9gFxs1PC6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fx9gFxs1PC6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Weatherman%20Shubham%20(%40shubhamtorres09)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshubhamtorres09%2Fstatus%2F1712375650084897016%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20assess%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20property%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20it%20will%20take%20another%2010-20%20days%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20much%20the%20cumulative%20impact%20of%20the%20devastation%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lepcha%20said%20in%20the%20online%20press%20conference%20conducted%20by%20Youth%20For%20Himalaya%2C%20a%20group%20of%20environmentalists%20from%20several%20Himalayan%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%203%2C%20a%20possible%20glacial%20landslide%20or%20cloudburst%20(the%20reason%20is%20still%20being%20debated)%20triggered%20a%20Glacial%20Lake%20Outburst%20Flood%20(GLOF)%20of%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20just%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0169555X21001914%5C%22%3E60%20kilometres%20upstream%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Teesta-III%20dam%20at%20Chungthang.%20The%20reservoir%20of%20the%20dam%20was%20already%20full%20and%20the%20flash%20flood%20that%20followed%20after%20the%20GLOF%20swept%20away%20the%20Teesta-III%20dam%20in%20minutes%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%204.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsikkim-flash-flood-toll-rises-to-37-inclement-weather-hampers-air-evacuation%2F668937.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20October%2011%2C%20nearly%2040%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20around%2080%20more%20are%20missing.%20However%2C%20inclement%20weather%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20is%20hampering%20rescue%20operations.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20evacuated%20461%20tourists%20from%20flash%20flood-hit%20towns%20in%20North%20Sikkim%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fiaf-evacuates-461-more-tourists-from-north-sikkim%2F669598.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-disaster-vimal-khawas-interview-himalaya%5C%22%3EHuman%20Failure%20One%20of%20Many%20Reasons%20for%20Sikkim%20Disaster%3B%20Lots%20of%20Work%2C%20Planning%20Ahead%3A%20Local%20Scientist%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMan-made%20disaster%2C%20not%20natural%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20current%20narrative%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20disaster%20but%20this%20is%20clearly%20not%20one%2C%20said%20Lepcha.%20The%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20burst%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20why%20did%20that%20happen%2C%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLakes%20don%E2%80%99t%20burst%20just%20like%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lepcha%20said%2C%20in%20the%20online%20press%20conference%20on%20October%2012.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20natural%20phenomenon%E2%80%A6%20climate%20change%20is%20not%20a%20natural%20disaster%2C%20but%20a%20man-made%20one%E2%80%A6governments%20have%20to%20accept%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EScientists%20and%20researchers%20have%20repeatedly%20identified%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20glacial%20lake%20as%20among%20the%20few%20that%20are%20under%20threat%20of%20a%20GLOF%20event.%20However%2C%20experts%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-disaster-vimal-khawas-interview-himalaya%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20warnings%20were%20never%20heeded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20parties%20are%20engaging%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblame%20game%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20dam%2C%20nobody%20is%20talking%20about%20how%20the%20location%20of%20the%20dam%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20lap%20of%20the%20mountain%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20Lepcha%20said.%20The%20dam%20is%20about%2060%20kilometres%20from%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20and%20the%20location%20itself%20is%20a%20mistake%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20totally%20a%20man-made%20disaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELepcha%20also%20called%20for%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20among%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20to%20stop%20building%20dams%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20biggest%20dam%20failure%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20noise%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20exclaimed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20come%20together%20as%20one%20voice%20to%20save%20the%20Himalaya%20%E2%80%93%20even%20take%20to%20the%20roads%20if%20necessary%2C%20because%20it%20is%20time%20for%20that%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20the%20Teesta%20has%20reclaimed%20her%20glory%20and%20we%20still%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20still%20continue%20ignoring%20the%20environmental%20and%20ecological%20challenges%20given%20our%20fragile%20ecology%20and%20topography%E2%80%A6%20today%20it%20was%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Teesta%2C%20tomorrow%20it%20will%20be%20something%20else%E2%80%A6%20they%20will%20come%20back%20and%20hit%20us%E2%80%A6then%20the%20whole%20extinction%20of%20the%20Sikkim%20Himalaya%20is%20on%20our%20doorstep.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocal%20activists%20have%20called%20on%20people%20across%20the%20country%20to%20conduct%20%E2%80%9CNational%20Climate%20Strikes%E2%80%9D%20on%20October%2015%20to%20express%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12171224%2FF7kYy-sakAAkPZ8.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12171224%2FF7kYy-sakAAkPZ8.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12171224%2FF7kYy-sakAAkPZ8-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12171224%2FF7kYy-sakAAkPZ8-1024x684.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESikkim%20chief%20minister%20P.S.%20Tamang.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40%40PSTamangGolay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EQuestions%20about%20dam%20operation%20and%20safety%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHimanshu%20Thakkar%2C%20coordinator%20of%20the%20South%20Asia%20Network%20on%20Dams%2C%20Rivers%20and%20People%20(SANDRP)%20said%20that%20dams%20act%20as%20a%20force%20multiplier%20in%20times%20of%20disaster%20and%20that%20this%20was%20observed%20during%20the%202013%20Uttarakhand%20floods%20also.%20The%20quantum%20of%20destruction%20increases%20when%20there%20is%20a%20dam%20and%20it%20is%20people%20at%20the%20sites%20of%20these%20dams%20who%20lose%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20the%20highest%20economic%20loss%20occurs%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20disaster%20occurs%2C%20Thakkar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20of%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20has%20been%20increasing%20since%20the%201960s%20and%20was%20a%20known%20source%20of%20a%20GLOF%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thakkar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0169555X21001914%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20glacier%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20retreating%20glaciers%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20%E2%80%9Chas%20become%20the%20largest%20and%20fastest-growing%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20spillway%20of%20the%20Teesta-III%20dam%20was%20not%20built%20to%20accommodate%20excess%20water%20from%20a%20GLOF.%20If%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20dam%20were%20opened%20in%20time%2C%20the%20reservoir%20would%20have%20been%20empty%20and%20the%20excess%20water%20from%20the%20GLOF%20may%20have%20been%20contained%20by%20the%20dam.%20The%20first%20alarm%20was%20raised%20by%20an%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20officer%20at%2010%3A30%20pm%20on%20October%203%20and%20the%20information%20was%20passed%20to%20his%20commander%20in%20Gangtok%20immediately%20and%20to%20Chungthang%20by%2010%3A50%20pm.%20However%2C%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20dam%20were%20still%20not%20operated%20in%20time.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20existence%20of%20an%20Early%20Warning%20System%20would%20have%20decreased%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20GLOF%20and%20the%20dam%20may%20even%20have%20been%20saved%2C%20and%20the%20downstream%20destruction%20averted%2C%20Thakkar%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDam%20operation%20is%20crucial%20under%20such%20circumstances.%20However%2C%20the%20Dam%20Safety%20Act%20of%202021%20focuses%20only%20on%20the%20structural%20safety%20of%20the%20dam%20and%20not%20operational%20safety%2C%20said%20Thakkar.%20The%20latter%20is%20extremely%20important%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Act%2C%20he%20added.%20Similarly%2C%20information%20about%20dam%20safety%20must%20be%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20there%20is%20a%20dire%20need%20to%20include%20independent%20dam%20experts%20in%20committees%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20government%20officials%2C%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDecommissioning%20a%20dam%20should%20also%20be%20included%20as%20part%20of%20a%20dam%E2%80%99s%20life%20cycle%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20the%20people%20should%20fight%20for%20this%20%E2%80%93%20otherwise%20people%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20it%2C%20as%20does%20the%20environment%E2%80%9D%2C%20Thakkar%20said.%20However%2C%20this%20does%20not%20figure%20in%20the%20Dam%20Safety%20Act%20at%20all%20and%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20dam%20safety%2C%20acts%20more%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Clobby%20for%20dams%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20alleged%20during%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSafety%20audit%20%5Bof%20dams%5D%20should%20be%20a%20public%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20commented%20Manshi%20Asher%2C%20while%20adding%20that%20there%20are%20500%20to%20900%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20upper%20Sutlej%20alone.%20Asher%20is%20co-founder%20of%20Himdhara%2C%20an%20NGO%20operating%20in%20Uttarakhand%20that%20has%20also%20been%20witnessing%20several%20mega%20infrastructure%20projects%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20local%20people%20and%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENewly%20installed%20cameras%20stopped%20working%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20October%2012%2C%20the%20NDMA%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20installed%20two%20solar-powered%20twin-camera%20Automated%20Weather%20Stations%20on%20two%20%E2%80%9Chigh-risk%E2%80%9D%20glacial%20lakes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20and%20Shako%20Cho%20%E2%80%93%20in%20upper%20Sikkim%20on%20September%2016.%20However%2C%20per%20the%20release%2C%20the%20equipment%20at%20South%20Lhonak%20%E2%80%9Cceased%20transmission%E2%80%9D%20after%20September%2019.%20%E2%80%9CAn%20ITBP%20contingent%20checked%20the%20equipment%20on%20September%2028%20as%20physically%20stable%2C%20but%20it%20could%20not%20be%20revived%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20now%20recommended%20in%20the%20release%20that%20the%20GLOF%20Risk%20Mitigation%20Programme%20be%20%E2%80%9Cextended%20to%20high-risk%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20A%202020%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnidm.gov.in%2FPDF%2Fpubs%2FNDMA%2F28.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edocument%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20policymakers%20by%20the%20NDMA%20had%20already%20recommended%20that%20a%20task%20committee%20be%20formulated%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdraft%20specific%20regulations%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cincreased%20risk%E2%80%9D%20of%20future%20GLOF%20events%20and%20that%20it%20give%20its%20recommendations%20within%20a%20year.%20It%20also%20announced%20in%20the%20same%20document%20that%20the%20NDMA%20has%20%E2%80%9Cproposed%20to%20take%20up%20a%20Comprehensive%20National%20GLOF%20Mitigation%20Project%20(CNGMP)%20whose%20aims%20and%20objectives%20will%20be%20developed%20and%20finalized%20in%20due%20course%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fafter-sikkim-flash-flood-government-to-bring-framework-for-national-glof-risk-mitigation-measures-soon%2Farticleshow%2F104379880.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Friday%20quoting%20anonymous%20sources%20noted%20that%20the%20GLOF%20and%20resulting%20devastation%20in%20Sikkim%20has%20prompted%20the%20government%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%E2%80%9Ca%20comprehensive%20GLOF%20Risk%20Mitigation%20Measure%E2%80%9D.%20The%20framework%20for%20this%20will%20be%20discussed%20at%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20in%20the%20coming%20week%2C%20it%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2011%2C%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20apex%20green%20court%20%E2%80%93%20also%20took%20up%20a%20suo%20moto%20case%20against%20the%20government%20of%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20public%20sector%20hydropower%20company%20NHPC%20and%20Sikkim%20Urja%20Limited%20(which%20operated%20the%20Teesta-III%20dam)%20based%20on%20a%20news%20story%20published%