t%20%E2%80%9Cto%20change%20the%20Middle%20East%E2%80%9D%20and%20defence%20minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%E2%80%99s%20threat%20that%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20will%20never%20go%20back%20to%20what%20it%20was%E2%80%9D%20are%20implemented%2C%20Israel%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20brink%20of%20a%20wider%20war%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F4rxjT1jKqsQ%3Fsi%3DkMs7n24naUZR9o5R%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20very%20disturbing%20and%20depressing%20picture%20that%20he%20is%20painting%20of%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20prospects%2C%20Levy%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20realism%20Israel%20needs%20a%20miracle%E2%80%9D%20adding%20the%20chances%20of%20that%20are%20very%20small.%20He%20said%20that%20people%20are%20in%20denial%20of%20their%20treatment%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20they%20have%20played%20with%20fire%20for%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELevy%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20bears%20very%20great%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happened%20and%20he%20must%20pay%20the%20price.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20moving%20steadily%2C%20if%20not%20acceleratedly%2C%20towards%20a%20climatic%20denouement%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20this%20morning%20announced%20that%20Israel%20wants%20all%20of%20Gaza%20north%20of%20Wadi%20Gaza%20to%20be%20vacated%20in%2024%20hours.%20That%E2%80%99s%201.1%20million%20people.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20told%20these%20Gazans%20to%20evacuate%20to%20the%20south%20and%20only%20return%20when%20they%20are%20permitted%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20way%20Israel%20has%20treated%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20over%20the%20last%20several%20years%20or%20decades%2C%20he%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20fire%20at%20innocent%20people%2C%20take%20out%20people%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20and%20smash%20their%20faces%2C%20expel%2C%20confiscate%2C%20rob%2C%20grab%20people%20from%20their%20beds%2C%20carry%20out%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20continue%20with%20the%20unbelievable%20siege%20of%20the%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20and%20everything%20will%20be%20alright.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Levy%20asks%20of%20all%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%20just%20those%20of%20Gaza%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20is%20it%20possible%20to%20forget%20that%20these%20are%20human%20beings%20whose%20ancestors%20were%20expelled%20from%20their%20land%20and%20placed%20in%20refugee%20camps%20where%20they%20would%20remain%3F%20These%20were%20human%20beings%20whom%20Israel%20dispossessed%20and%20expelled%2C%20whom%20it%20conquered%20again%20in%20their%20land%20of%20refuge%20and%20then%20turned%20into%20animals%20in%20a%20cage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20do%20so%2C%20Levy%20asks%3A%20%E2%80%9CWill%20Israel%20learn%20its%20lesson%3F%20No.%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20threats%20of%20%E2%80%98flattening%20Gaza%E2%80%99%20prove%20only%20one%20thing%3A%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20learned%20a%20thing.%20The%20arrogance%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20even%20though%20Israel%20is%20paying%20a%20high%20price%20once%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697201632000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13182007%2FKT-13-oct-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-invading-gaza-israels-biggest-ever-war-crime-haaretz-columnist-gideon-levy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20Levey%20says%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20are%20in%20denial%20of%20their%20treatment%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20they%20have%20played%20with%20fire%20for%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades.%22%2C%22aut