Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeven%20FIRs%20were%20slapped%20against%20the%20news%20portal%E2%80%99s%20reporter%2C%20Jaalam%20Singh%2C%20within%20a%20span%20of%20four%20days%20(September%207-10).%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20a%20total%20of%2011%20FIRs%20were%20filed%2C%20back-to-back%2C%20in%20the%20Guna%20and%20Shivpuri%20districts%20of%20the%20Gwalior%20division.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20laying%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20state%20media%20centre%20on%20October%203%2C%20Chouhan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOfficeofSSC%2Fstatus%2F1709130355913957821%3Ft%3DZtbKUr6BrAnQR6Pw_w7H6Q%26s%3D19%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20several%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20including%20a%20fellowship%20for%20women%20scribes%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20committee%20to%20frame%20a%20journalists%E2%80%99%20protection%20law%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20and%20ensured%20advertisements%20for%20small%20newspapers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaalam%20Singh%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D3359685804280083%26set%3Dpb.100007160882722.-2207520000%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20an%20objectionable%20video%20that%20had%20surfaced%20on%20September%207.%20Without%20mentioning%20anybody%2C%20the%20journalist%20wrote%20that%20a%20video%20and%20messages%20of%20a%20respected%20politician%20who%20changed%20parties%20have%20surfaced%20and%20have%20reached%20the%20high%20command.%20His%20report%20said%20that%20the%20politician%E2%80%99s%20ticket%20may%20be%20cancelled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20was%20allegedly%20taken%20as%20an%20offence%20by%20the%20supporters%20of%20the%20state%20minister%20of%20panchayat%20and%20development%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Sisodia.%20The%20individuals%20associated%20with%20right-wing%20organisations%20and%20supporters%20of%20the%20minister%20filed%20different%20FIRs%20at%20different%20police%20stations%20accusing%20the%20journalist%20of%20tarnishing%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20image%20and%20blackmailing%20him.%20However%2C%20there%20were%20other%20FIRs%20by%20civilians%20accusing%20the%20reporter%20of%20blackmailing%20and%20extorting%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20arrested%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Kota%20on%20September%2013.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20applied%20for%20anticipatory%20bail%2C%20Singh%20had%20to%20surrender%20when%20the%20application%20was%20rejected.%20He%20is%20still%20in%20jail%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20advocate%20informed%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMinister%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Sisodia%20won%20the%20Bamori%20assembly%20elections%20in%202013%20and%202018%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket.%20He%20was%20the%20minister%20of%20labour%20in%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20cabinet.%20Sisodia%20was%20among%20the%2022%20MLAs%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmp-govt-teeters-as-scindia-22-mlas-quit-cong-to-join-bjp%2Farticleshow%2F74567759.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20with%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20to%20join%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20He%20won%20the%20by-elections%20in%202020%20and%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20panchayat%20and%20rural%20development%20Cabinet%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-lack-of-representation-muslim-community-alienated%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3A%20With%20Lack%20of%20Representation%2C%20Muslim%20Community%20Feels%20Disillusioned%20and%20Alienated%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESisodia%E2%80%99s%20name%20had%20hit%20the%20headlines%20in%20January%202023%20for%20threatening%20Congress%20party%20members%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2Fmp-minister-mahendra-singh-sisodia-says-join-bjp-or-else-cms-bulldozer-is-ready-stokes-controversy%2Farticleshow%2F97143218.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebulldozer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20action%20if%20they%20did%20not%20join%20the%20BJP.%20His%20ticket%20has%20been%20withheld%20in%20the%20elections%20that%20are%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2017%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETown%20Inspector%20of%20Guna%20Anup%20Bhargava%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20media%20is%20questioning%20the%20police%20action%20without%20knowing%20that%20the%20individual%20does%20not%20have%20good%20conduct.%20He%20has%20a%20system%20of%20blackmailing%20and%20extorting%20money%20even%20from%20Anganwadi%20workers.%20Local%20media%20would%20have%20supported%20him%20if%20he%20was%20a%20good%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20party%20worker%20filed%20a%20complaint%20in%20our%20area%20based%20on%20a%20paper%20cutting%20on%20WhatsApp%20for%20maligning%20the%20image%20of%20the%20party.%20It%20did%20not%20mention%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20name.%20So%20we%20served%20him%20a%20notice%20because%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%20We%20did%20not%20send%20him%20to%20jail%20in%20any%20matter.%20However%2C%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20different%20police%20stations%20of%20the%20district%20including%20Fatehgarh%20and%20Myena%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bhargava.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Suman%20Kirar%20refuted%20the%20accusations%20of%20blackmailing%20against%20her%20husband.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20has%20been%20in%20this%20profession%20for%20ten%20years.%20He%20has%20worked%20with%20LiveTV%20and%20Swades%20as%20well.%20How%20does%20he%20suddenly%20become%20a%20blackmailer%20after%20filing%20a%20report%20against%20the%20minister%3F%20He%20is%20innocent.%20The%20charges%20framed%20against%20him%20are%20fake.%20It%20has%20almost%20been%20a%20month%20since%20his%20arrest.%20How%20long%20will%20they%20keep%20him%20imprisoned%3F%20The%20journalists%20have%20left%20him%20alone%20in%20this%20ordeal.%20Is%20this%20not%20harassment%3F%20The%20FIRs%20against%20him%20must%20be%20quashed%20and%20he%20should%20be%20released%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvocate%20Manohar%20Mirota%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20nine%20FIRs%20were%20registered%20against%20the%20reporter%20in%20Guna%20district%20alone.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20applied%20for%20anticipatory%20bail%20which%20was%20rejected.%20The%20order%20was%20leaked%20to%20the%20general%20public%20half%20an%20hour%20before%20the%20official%20order%20was%20pronounced%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirota%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshivraj-singhs-profligacy-in-poll-year-brings-debt-ridden-mp-to-the-brink-of-bankruptcy%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Profligacy%20in%20Poll%20Year%20Brings%20Debt-Ridden%20MP%20to%20the%20Brink%20of%20Bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20unconfirmed%2C%20we%20are%20getting%20information%20that%20at%20least%2021%20FIRs%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20one%20in%20Chattisgarh%20have%20been%20registered%20against%20Singh.%20We%20have%20succeeded%20in%20securing%20bail%20in%20two%20FIRs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDainik%20Khulasa%E2%80%99s%20editor%20Suresh%20Acharya%20condemned%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20arrest.%20While%20supporting%20their%20reporter%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20a%20journalist%20to%20break%20the%20news%20that%20sometimes%20triggers%20those%20in%20power.%20%E2%80%9COur%20reporter%20did%20not%20create%20fake%20news.%20It%20was%20based%20on%20an%20objectionable%20video%20in%20which%20a%20female%20leader%20was%20also%20involved.%20Being%20a%20public%20representative%2C%20it%20does%20not%20suit%20a%20minister%20to%20indulge%20in%20such%20objectionable%20conduct.%20Does%20it%20mean%20that%20female%20leaders%20are%20also%20not%20safe%20in%20your%20party%3F%20An%20FIR%20should%20be%20registered%20against%20him%20for%20muzzling%20the%20truth.%20This%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20right%20to%20press%20freedom%20of%20a%20journalist%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20Acharya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcharya%20added%20that%20the%20administration%20registered%20FIRs%20because%20of%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20close%20relations%20with%20Scindia.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20informed%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2F11-firs-in-4-days-mp-journalist-targeted-for-report-on-bjp-minister%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520trigger%2520seemed%2520to%2520be%2Cminister%2520he%2520didn%2527t%2520name.%26amp%3Btext%3DWhen%2520a%2520journalist%2520in%2520Madhya%2Cthat%2520he%2520would%2520be%2520arrested%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecomplainants%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20FIR%20do%20not%20even%20know%20Singh.%20Even%20the%20local%20media%20has%20avoided%20taking%20any%20stand%20with%20him%20due%20to%20political%20pressure.%20We%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20home%20minister%2C%20and%20the%20commissioner%20in%20this%20regard.%20They%20have%20assured%20us%20an%20independent%20investigation%20while%20pressing%20that%20arresting%20without%20proper%20investigation%20must%20have%20been%20avoided%2C%E2%80%9D%20Acharya%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Guna%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Rakesh%20Sakar%2C%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20FIRs%20can%20be%20identified%20by%20compiling%20all%20the%20FIRs%20in%20different%20districts.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20accused%20has%20a%20criminal%20record.%20However%2C%20a%20case%20should%20not%20be%20registered%20without%20proper%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sakar%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EState%20of%20press%20freedom%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20YouTube%20journalist%20along%20with%20seven%20theatre%20artists%20and%20two%20others%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fwhy-a-journalist-7-theatre-artistes-were-attacked-paraded-in-underwear-by-madhya-pradesh-police-6257944e92be1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20police%20for%20staging%20a%20protest%20outside%20a%20police%20station%20in%20April%202022.%20The%20photos%20of%20these%20men%20went%20viral%20standing%20inside%20the%20police%20station%20and%20seated%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20a%20lock-up%2C%20wearing%20only%20their%20underpants%2C%20were%20widely%20circulated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20was%20listed%20third%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rightsrisks.org%2Fpress-release%2Fpress-release-194-journalists-targeted-eight-killed-during-2022-in-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehighest%20number%20of%20attacks%20against%20journalists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%202021%20report%20by%20a%20Delhi-based%20think%20tank.%20of%20the%20Group.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20mentioned%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20total%20of%20194%20journalists%2C%20including%20seven%20women%2C%20who%20were%20targeted%20in%20various%20incidents%20across%20India%20during%202022%20by%20state%20agencies%20to%20non-state%20political%20actors%20and%20criminals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20armed%20opposition%20groups%20(AOGs).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Day%20(May%203)%2C%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20(RSF