0it%20could%20encircle%20the%20entire%20Panjim%20market.%20We%20even%20organised%20a%20procession%20where%20we%20carried%20this%20chain%20to%20the%20Mandovi%20river%2C%20which%20is%20next%20to%20the%20market%20area%2C%20and%20it%20extended%20for%20around%20one%20kilometre.%20We%20also%20crafted%20masks%20from%20these%20bags%2C%20referring%20to%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98plastic%20monsters%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20created%20posters%20among%20other%20activities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20were%20there%20for%2021%20days%2C%20we%20observed%20many%20people%20beginning%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20stitched%20cloth%20bags.%20We%20also%20noticed%20that%20many%20of%20them%20returned%20with%20our%20Maka%20Naka%20bags%20during%20their%20next%20shopping%20trip!%20Even%20small%20changes%20like%20this%20are%20a%20significant%20achievement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhandelwal%20shares%20that%20to%20date%2C%20the%20campaign%20has%20made%20approximately%20one%20lakh%20cloth%20bags%2C%20prevented%2070%2C000%20garments%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%20and%20saved%20about%20two%20million%20plastic%20bags%20from%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20these%20bags%20is%20a%20challenging%20task%2C%20requiring%20tailors%20to%20carefully%20choose%20the%20right%20fabric%20for%20each%20bag%E2%80%99s%20size%20and%20shape%20while%20ensuring%20they%20look%20appealing.%20The%20tailors%20involved%20in%20this%20project%20are%20mostly%20women%20from%20various%20self-help%20groups.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20around%2072%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20tailors%2C%20Sangeeta%20Chari%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20people%20continue%20using%20these%20bags%20which%20we%20stitch%2C%20Goa%20will%20soon%20become%20plastic-free.%E2%80%9D%20She%20informs%20that%20earlier%2C%20she%20used%20to%20pursue%20tailoring%20as%20a%20hobby%2C%20but%20now%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20source%20of%20income%20for%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20make%20bags%20from%20the%20fabric%20given%20to%20us%20and%20get%20Rs%2010%20per%20bag.%20I%20believe%20this%20is%20profitable%20as%20one%20gets%20to%20do%20a%20job%20by%20sitting%20at%20home%20while%20earning%20some%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20these%20bags%20for%20free%20(or%20%E2%80%98pay%20as%20you%20like%E2%80%99)%20at%20select%20Goan%20markets%20as%20part%20of%20the%20campaign.%20They%20are%20also%20sold%20to%20brands%2C%20government%20organisations%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMaka-Naka-Plastic-campaign-in-schools_11zon_11zon-1697030256.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20children%20actively%20participating%20in%20the%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20campaign%20to%20promote%20cloth%20bags.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMaka-Naka-Plastic-campaign-in-schools_11zon_11zon-1697030256.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMaka-Naka-Plastic-campaign-in-schools_11zon_11zon-1697030256-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMaka-Naka-Plastic-campaign-in-schools_11zon_11zon-1697030256-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMaka-Naka-Plastic-campaign-in-schools_11zon_11zon-1697030256-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMaka-Naka-Plastic-campaign-in-schools_11zon_11zon-1697030256-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332041%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchool%20children%20actively%20participating%20in%20the%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20campaign%20to%20promote%20cloth%20bags.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20schools%20and%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20spread%20awareness%20and%20change%20the%20behaviour%20of%20consumers%20towards%20plastic%20use%2C%20Khandelwal%20has%20taken%20this%20campaign%20to%20local%20schools.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20initially%20launched%20the%20campaign%2C%20we%20believed%20that%20stitching%2010%2C000%20bags%20would%20address%20the%20issue.%20However%2C%20now%20that%20we%20have%20reached%20the%20milestone%20of%20creating%20one%20lakh%20cloth%20bags%2C%20we%20realise%20that%20we%20have%20only%20just%20begun.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20School%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20elaborates%20Khandelwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20covered%2034%20schools%20and%20engaged%203%2C400%20students%20in%20this%20campaign.%20They%20aim%20to%20reach%20around%2010%2C000%20students%20and%20establish%20a%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20chapter%20in%20each%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20schools%2C%20the%20campaign%20promotes%20collecting%20pre-loved%20fabric%20to%20create%20cloth%20bags%20and%20sell%20them%20to%20fund%20their%20eco%20clubs.%20Some%20schools%20are%20also%20designing%20posters%20and%20displaying%20them%20in%20public%20areas%2C%20such%20as%20shops%2C%20community%20halls%20and%20%3Cem%3Epanchayats%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Posters%20created%20by%20school%20students%20to%20support%20the%20campaign.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPosters-made-by-school-students-1697030588-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPosters%20created%20by%20school%20students%20to%20support%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20campaign%2C%20they%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Zero%20Posro%E2%80%99%20store%2C%20launched%20by%20Jonah%20Fernandes.%20This%20store%20strongly%20opposes%20plastic%20packaging%20and%20encourages%20customers%20to%20utilise%20reusable%20cloth%20bags%20or%20glass%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20tackling%20two%20issues%20here.%20First%2C%20we%20have%20noticed%20that%20only%20six%20percent%20of%20the%20produce%20is%20local%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20comes%20from%20neighbouring%20states.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20promote%20local%20and%20organic%20produce.%20Second%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20tackling%20the%20issue%20of%20plastic%20and%20dry%20waste.%20Around%2080%20percent%20of%20our%20household%20dry%20waste%2C%20such%20as%20plastic%2C%20glass%2C%20and%20paper%2C%20comes%20from%20our%20kitchens%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Khandelwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sensible%20Earth%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326377%2Fnoida-madhuri-balodi-amit-singh-kavi-the-poetry-art-project-glass-bottle-art-sustainability-home-decor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactively%20collecting%20glass%20jars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20having%20already%20collected%202%2C000%20with%20a%20target%20of%20reaching%2010%2C000.%20Khandelwal%20points%20out%20that%20recycling%20glass%20can%20have%20a%20higher%20environmental%20impact%2C%20so%2C%20they%20have%20launched%20a%20campaign%20to%20collect%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20store%20glass%20jars%20in%20collaboration%20with%20local%20self-help%20groups.%20They%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20repurpose%20these%20jars%20within%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhandelwal%20maintains%20that%20this%20battle%20with%20plastic%20or%20waste%2C%20in%20general%2C%20is%20a%20long-drawn%20affair%2C%20and%20there%20is%20an%20ongoing%20need%20to%20raise%20awareness.%20He%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20changing%20the%20perception%20of%20Goa%2C%20which%20is%20often%20solely%20associated%20with%20fun%20and%20enjoyment.%20This%20perception%20puts%20tremendous%20pressure%20on%20waste%20management%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20Goa%20receives%20four%20times%20more%20tourists%20than%20its%20actual%20population%20(15%20lakhs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20change%20the%20narrative%20of%20tourism%20in%20Goa.%20It%20is%20a%20biodiversity%20hotspot%2C%20an%20extremely%20fragile%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20one%20has%20to%20walk%20carefully%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khandelwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20Arti%20Das%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Arti%20Das.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2Fuploads%2Fplasticwaste%2FAnnual_Report_2019-20_PWM.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b