0%20grams%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250601%2Faarti-rastogi-bengaluru-food-startup-artinci-healthy-sugar-free-keto-friendly-gluten-free-desserts-ice-cream-brownies-cakes-hearing-disability-woman-entrepreneur-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esugar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20seven%20kilograms%20of%20milk.%20Otherwise%2C%20a%20sour%20taste%20develops%20during%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20preparation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Avijit%20is%20not%20daunted%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20so%20many%20units.%20%E2%80%9CMaa%20Kali%20Rabri%20Bhandar%20sells%20600%20kilograms%20of%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20day%20across%20Kolkata.%20We%20just%20focus%20on%20our%20legacy%20and%20the%20one%20Pannalal%20left%20behind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697030304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20villages%20of%20Ainya%20and%20Gangpur%20in%20West%20Bengal%20are%20collectively%20known%20as%20Rabrigram%20for%20their%20synonymity%20with%20the%20sweet.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20why%20their%20%E2%80%98rabri%E2%80%99%20deserves%20a%20GI%20tag!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331992%2Fmaa-kali-rabri-bhandar-avijit-patra-pannalal-kolkata-rabri-gi-tag-origin-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Railways%3A%20Job%20Openings%20at%20RITES%20for%20Engineers%2C%20Salary%20Upto%20Rs%205.5%20Lakh%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERail%20India%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Service%20(RITES)%20is%20inviting%20applications%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263873%2Findia-engineer-